\id ACT - SYN- Siyin Bible 
\ide 65001 - Unicode (UTF-8)
\h SAWLTAKTE 
\toc1 SAWLTAKTE 
\toc2 Sawltakte 
\toc3 Sawl 
\mt1 SAWLTAK TE  
\mt2 ACTS  
\c 1  
\s1 Tha Thiangtho Kamciam  
\p
\v 1 Theophilus awng, amasa laibu ka atna sungah, Jesus i sep le a hilna theampo a kipat pan in,   
\p
\v 2 Ama a ki lakto ni dong, tuazawk Tha Thiangtho tungtawn in a tealsa sawltak te tungah thupia hi:   
\p
\v 3 A thuak zawkciang in sawltak te in ni sawm li sung Ama mu uh a, Pathian kumpingam taw kisai thu te son hi, Ama nungta tatak hi, ci tetti kho tampi taw lak hi:   
\p
\v 4 Munkhat ah amate taw a ki kaikhop laitak in, Jerusalem pan koima pai ngawl tu in, \wj Keima tung pan na zaksa uh bangma in, Pa i kamciam na ngak vun.\wj*   
\p
\v 5 \wj Banghangziam cile John in tui taw tuiphumna hong pia takpi hi; ahihang ni tampi ma in Tha Thiangtho i tuiphumna na sang tu uh ci, \wj* ci in amate thupia hi.   
\s1 Jesus Van Ka  
\r Lk. 24:50-53  
\p
\v 6 Tua ahikom amate munkhat a ki kaikhop tek uh ciang in, sawltak te in Jesus kungah, Topa awng, tu in Israel te tungah kumpingam na piakik tu ziam? ci in dong uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Jesus in amate tung ah, \wj Pa in Ama vangletna sungah a koisa hun le ni te sia, note i heak tu kisam ngawl hi.\wj*   
\p
\v 8 \wj Ahihang note tungah Tha Thiangtho hong thet zawkciang in, vangletna na nga tu uh hi: taciang in Jerusalem le Judah ngamsung theampo, taciang Samaria ngamsung le lei mong a tawp dong in, keima tetti te na hi tu uh hi, \wj* ci hi.   
\p
\v 9 Taciang hi thu te a son zawkciang, amate in a et uh laitak in, Jesus sia a tungsang ah ki lato a; amate mutang in mei in lia hi.   
\p
\v 10 Tabang in vantung ah a kato sia mate in a et tek uh laitak in, en vun, amate hui ah puanpak sil in mi ni hong ding hi;   
\p
\v 11 Tua te in, no Galilee mite, banghang in vantung en in ding top lai nu ziam? note kung pan in van ah a ki lato na mu uh bangma in, hongpai kik tu hi, ci uh hi.   
\s1 Judas A Laitu Teal  
\p
\v 12 Tuazawkciang in amate Olive mual pan in Jerusalem ah heakkik uh hi, Olive mual sia Jerusalem pan in sabbath ni pai thei na tan khawng khuala hi.   
\p
\v 13 Jerusalem a thet uh ciang in, inn tung doituam ah kato tek uh a, tua mun ah, Peter, James le John, taciang Andrew, Philip le Thomas, Bartholomew le Matthew, Alphaeus tapa James, Simon Zealot, James naupa Judas te om uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Hiteng a vekpi lungkim in nupi te, Jesus nu Mary le a suapui te taw tatsat ngawl in thungen khawm tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 15 Taciang in Peter sia a nungzui te, mihing za le kul kiim i laizang ah ding a,   
\p
\v 16 U le nau te awng, Tha Thiangtho in David i kam zangin a sonkholsa, Jesus man tute a makai Judas thu taw kisai in hi laithiangtho sia a tangtun hamtang kul hi.   
\p
\v 17 Banghangziam cile ama sia eite taw a kisim khawm hi a, hi Pathian nasepna sungah panmun nga hi.   
\p
\v 18 Hisia pa in phatngawlna a vawt man taw lo ciing khat lei hi; taciang a lusuk nuailam in tak in, a pumpi kisantham a, a ngil zong ke keak hi.   
\p
\v 19 Hi thu sia Jerusalem ah a om theampo in he uh a; tua lo sia amate kam in, Akeldama, ci uh hi, a khiakna sia, thisan lo, a cinopna a hihi.   
\p
\v 20 Banghangziam cile, Psalm labu sungah, ama omna mun sia awngthong tahen a, a sungah kuama om heak tahen: taciang a nasep sia midang in la tahen, ci in ki atkhol hi.   
\p
\v 21 Tua ahikom Topa Jesus eite sungah sungtum le pusuak in a om hunsung theampo,   
\p
\v 22 John in tuiphumna a piakpan kipan, eite kung panvan ah a ki lakto ni dong, eite taw a omkhawm te sung pan khatpo sia thawkikna thu eite taw tetti a hi tu in, nasep piak hamtang tu a hihi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 23 Taciang amate in, Barsabas kici a, Justus zong a kici Joseph le Matthias te ni teal uh hi.   
\p
\v 24 Amate in, Topa awng, nangma in mi theampo i thinsung na he hi, hi te ni sung pan kua na teal ziam, ci hong lak tan,   
\p
\v 25 Tabang in ama in, thunit ngawlna hang in puk a, ama omna mun ah a pai Judas atu in, hi Pathian nasepna le sawltak te sungah kihel tu hi, ci in thungen khawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 26 Taciang amate in aisan uh a; aitang sia Matthias tungah tak hi; taciang ama sia sawltak sawm le khat te taw kisim khawm hi.   
\c 2  
\s1 Tha Thiangtho Theng  
\p
\v 1 Pentecost ni hong thet ciang in, amate a vekpi thukimtak in munkhat ah ki kaikhawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 2 Thakhatthu in van pan hui theau vapum bang aw nging hong theng a, amate to na inn hong dim hi.   
\p
\v 3 Taciang leii taw a kibang meikuang hong kilang a, amate khatsim tungah hong om hi.   
\p
\v 4 Amate a vekpi in Tha Thiangtho taw kidim uh a, Thaa in pau thei na a piak bang in, kam dang tek taw pau uh hi,   
\p
\v 5 Van nuai ngam tatuam pan in biakna sang a ki pumpiak Judah mite Jerusalem ah om uh hi.   
\p
\v 6 Tua aw a zak uh ciang in, mihonpi te hongpai ngawp uh a, amate i pauna sia amate kam tek taw za uh ahikom buai tek mama uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang amate a vekpi in lungmang in lamdangsatek mama uh a, en vun, amate a vekpi uh in Galilee mite hi ngawl ziam?   
\p
\v 8 Bangbang in i pianpui kam tek taw za hi ziam?   
\p
\v 9 Eite sia Parthia ngam, Media ngam, Elam ngam, Mesopotamia ngam, Judah ngam, Cappadocia ngam, Pontus ngam, Asia ngam,   
\p
\v 10 Phrygia ngam, Pamphylia ngam, Egypt ngam le Libya ngam Syrene khua pan i hi a, Rome sung leangna te, Judah mite le Judah biakna a bia Gentile te,   
\p
\v 11 Cretes le Arabia ngam pan i hi a, amate i eima kam in a pau i zak sia Pathian i a lamdang nasep na hi, ci in khat le khat ki sason uh hi.   
\p
\v 12 Amate a vekpi in lamdangsa mama uh a, lungmang mama in, hi thu sia a bang khiakna peuma ziam? ci in khat le khat ki dong uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 A dang te in selno in, hite sia sapittui thak kham hon uh, ci uh hi.   
\s1 Peter in Thuhil  
\p
\v 14 Ahihang Peter sia a dang sawm le khat te taw ding uh a, aw ngingtak in amate tung ah, no Judah mite le Jerusalem ah a omte, hi thu he tavun a, ka pau te ngai vun:   
\p
\v 15 Banghangziam cile hite sia no i ngaisut bang in kham ngawl hi, zingsang nai kua hi pheang hi.   
\p
\v 16 Ahihang hi thu sia kamsang Joel i sonkholsa;   
\p
\v 17 Pathian in ni tawpkhak ni ciang in, mi theampo tungah ka Thaa ka buak tu hi: taciang na tapa te le na tanu te in maisang thu pualak tu uh hi, taciang na tangval te in mangmu tu uh hi, taciang na puhuai te uh in mangman tu uh hi:   
\p
\v 18 Tua ni ciang in, ka salpa le salnu te tungah ka Thaa ka buak tu a; amate in mailam thu pualak tu hi:   
\p
\v 19 Taciang vantung ah nalamdang te ahizong, lei nuai ah thisan, mei le meikhu musakna te ahizong, ka lak tu hi:   
\p
\v 20 A thupi le a cepte tak Topa ni hong thet ma in, ni hong mial tu a, tha zong thisan suak tu hi:   
\p
\v 21 Tua hun ciang in a kuamapo Topa min a sam theampo in ngupna nga tu hi.   
\p
\v 22 No Israel mite, hi thu te ngai vun; Nazareth mi Jesus sia, Pathian in note sungah a tumdang nate, nalamdang te le musakna te taw tettipang in a kipsak mihing a hihi, note mama in zong na heak uh bangma in:   
\p
\v 23 Ama sia, Pathian i khensat sa ngaisutna le heakkholsa bang in ki ap hi, taciang note in na man uh a, a seksol khut taw thinglamte tungah khai in na that uh hi:   
\p
\v 24 Ama sia thina in a letcip tu suakthei ngawl ahikom, Pathian in thokiksak a, thina ngimthuak na pan in suaktasak hi.   
\p
\v 25 Banghangziam cile David in Ama taw kisai in a son na ah, Topa sia a tawntung in ka mai ah ka mukhol hi, banghangziam cile Ama sia ka ziatsang ah om a, bangma in hong linglawngsak zo batu hi:   
\p
\v 26 Tua ahikom ka thinsung ah nopna om a, ka lei a lungdam hi; tuabek domngawl ka taksa zong lametna sungah tawlnga tu hi:   
\p
\v 27 Banghangziam cile nangma in ka tha sia hell sungah na nusia bua hi, na Mi Thiangtho sia a muatcip tu na oai bua hi.   
\p
\v 28 Nangma in nuntakna lampi te nong hesak zo a; na maitang taw lungdamna dim in nong vawt tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 29 Ka suapui te awng, minam te i pa David thu hangsan tak in kong son tu hi, ama sia thi a kivui zo hi, taciang tuni dong eite taw a than om nginge hi.   
\p
\v 30 Ama in cilesa lam a suanlepal te sung pan, Pathian in Christ sia thokiksak tu a, kumpi tokhum tungah tosak tu hi, ci in kiciamna taw a kamciam na sia kamsang a hi nataw in he hi;   
\p
\v 31 Hi Christ thawkikna a mukhol hu in, a tha sia hell ah nusia ngawl hi, a taksa zong muat ngawl hi, ci son hi.   
\p
\v 32 Hi Jesus sia Pathian in thokiksak zo a, kote sia a tetti te ka hi uh hi.   
\p
\v 33 Tua ahikom Pathian i ziatsang ah ki lamsang a, Pa i kamciam Tha Thiangtho a san hu in, tu in na mu uh le na zak uh te sia Ama i hong buak a hihi.   
\p
\v 34 Banghangziam cile David sia van ah kato ngawl hi: ahihang ama vateak in, Topa in ka Topa kungah, ka ziatsang ah to in,   
\p
\v 35 Na ngalte ka peang koina in ka vawt mateng, ci hi.   
\p
\v 36 Tua ahikom Israel minam theampo in thiangtak in tel tavun, thinglamte tungah na khai uh Jesus sia Pathian in Topa le Christ in vawt zo hi.   
\p
\v 37 Tu in amate in hi thu a zak uh ciang in, amate i thinsung hol a, Peter le adang sawltak te kungah, U le nau te awng, banglaw tu khu ziam? ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 38 Taciang in Peter in amate tung ah, na mawna uh kisik vun a, na mawna uh hang in na vekpi Jesus Christ min taw tui ki phum vun, taciang Tha Thiangtho letsong na nga tu uh hi.   
\p
\v 39 Banghangziam cile kamciam sia noma, na tate, taciang a khuala mi theampo le Topa i Pathian in a sap tu theampo atu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 40 Peter in a dang kammal tampi taw tettipang in hanthawn a, hi minam seksol te kung pan in noma le noma ki ngum vun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 41 Tuazawkciang in Peter thuhilna sia lungdamtak in a sang te tui ki phum uh hi: taciang tua ni ma in mihing tul thum kiim amate kungah ki belap hi.   
\p
\v 42 Amate sia sawltak te hilna le ki pawlkhopna, anluum bal na le thungetna ah tatsat ngawl in kiptak in om uh hi.   
\p
\v 43 Sawltak te in nalamdang tampi le musakna tampi vawt uh a, mi theampo tungah launa hong theng hi.   
\p
\v 44 Taciang a umte theampo ki kaikhawm uh a, a neisa theampo zong neikhawm uh hi;   
\p
\v 45 Amate neisa le van te zuak uh a, mi khatsim i a kisapna bang in, mi theampo tungah hawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 46 Amate sia nisim tatsat ngawl in biakinn sungah thukim in om tek uh hi, taciang inn khat zawk inn khat ah anluum te bal uh a, lungdamtak le thin ki si lung kisi in an ne khawm tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 47 Pathian pok khawm tek uh a, mi theampo taw maipha nga uh hi. Ngupna nga mi Topa in nisim in pawlpi sungah belap hi.   
\c 3  
\s1 Peangbaipa Dam  
\p
\v 1 Tu in Peter le John te thunget hun nitak sang nai thum ciang in biakinn ah pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 2 A nu ngil sung pan ma in a peangbai khat sia midang te in toai a, biakinn sung a tum te tung pan huna ngen tu in, Hoi, a kici biakinn kongpi ah nisim in koi uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Ama in Peter le John te biakinn sung a tum tu a mu ciang in huna ngen hi.   
\p
\v 4 Taciang Peter in, John taw phatak in en a, hong en tan, ci hi.   
\p
\v 5 Amate tung pan in khatpo nga tu lamen in phatak in en hi.   
\p
\v 6 Peter in, dangka le kham bangma nei ngawl khi hi; ahihang ka neisun kong pia hi: Nazareth mi Jesus Christ min taw ding in a, lampai in, ci hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang Peter in tua pa ziatsang khut pan len a, kaito hi: tasia pociang tua pa i peang le a ngumit te thakho kik hi.   
\p
\v 8 Ama sia tawnkawm in ding hi, taciang lampai a, biakinn sungah amate taw tum hi, taciang lampai kawm tawnkawm in Pathian pok hi.   
\p
\v 9 Taciang lampai in Pathian a pok mi theampo in mu uh hi:   
\p
\v 10 Ama sia biakinn ah, Hoi, a kici kongpi ah to in hu na a ngen pa hi, ci a he uh hi: taciang hisia pa tungah thupiang te lamdangsa in lungman na taw dim uh hi.   
\s1 Peter Thuhilna  
\p
\v 11 A peangbai na pan a dam pa in Peter le John te beal a, mi theampo in lamdangsa in amate kung, Solomon buk sangah tai lialua uh hi.   
\p
\v 12 Tua thu Peter in a mu ciang in amate tung ah, no Israel mite awng, banghang in hi thu lamdangsa nu ziam? a hibale banghang in hisia pa sia koma vang le thianthona hang in lampai bang in, hong en cinten nu ziam?   
\p
\v 13 Abraham, Isaac le Jacob te Pathian, i pu le pa te Pathian in, a Tapa Jesus sia vangliansak zo hi; Ama na ap uh a, Pilate in thakik nuam napi, note in Pilate mai ah na nial uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Note in Mi Thiangtho le Mi Thutang pa na nial uh a, tualthat pa note tungah piak tu in na dei uh hi;   
\p
\v 15 Taciang nuntakna Topa na that uh hi, Ama sia Pathian in thina pan in thokiksak a; kote sia a tetti te ka hi uh hi.   
\p
\v 16 Jesus min upna tungtawn in hisia pa na mu uh le na heak uh bang in, Ama min taw hatsak hi: hi hi, a upna hang in hi damna kicing sia note theampo mai ah pia hi.   
\p
\v 17 Tu in ka suapui te awng, noma le na makai te in Jesus tungah na vawt uh te, na heak ngawl uh hu in a vawt na hi uh hi, ci ka he hi.   
\p
\v 18 Ahihang tua thu te sia, Pathian in kamsang te kam tungtawn in hong lakkholsa, Christ sia thuak tu hi, ci thu a tangtun natu a hihi.   
\p
\v 19 Tua ahikom note na mawna uh ki sikkik vun a, na thinsung uh ki kheal vun, tabang in na mawna uh te hong phiatsak tu a, Topa mai pan in tha thak na nga uh hun hong thengkik tu hi.   
\p
\v 20 Taciang note tungah a ki pualaksa Jesus Christ hongpaisak tu hi:   
\p
\v 21 Leitung pian pan kipan Pathian in Ama kamsang thiangtho te kam tungtawn in a sonkholsa bang in, na theampo thaksua na hun dong Jesus Christ sia vantung ah om suak tu hi.   
\p
\v 22 Banghangziam cile Moses in a tatak in, pu le pa te tung ah, Topa na Pathian in keima bang kamsang khat, na suapui te sung pan ka piangsak tu a; note tungah a sonsa theampo sia na theampo sungah na ngai tu uh hi.   
\p
\v 23 Taciang in kamsang thu a ngai nuam ngawl peuma, mipi sung pan in susia tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 24 Samuel pan kipan in a nungsang pan kamsang thu a son te theampo in, hi ni thu te sonkhol zo uh hi.   
\p
\v 25 Note sia kamsang te i tate na hi uh hi, Pathian in i pu le pa te taw Abraham kungah a vawt kamciam, na suanlepal tungtawn in leitung minam theampo in thupha sang tu hi, ci thu na sang tu uh hi.   
\p
\v 26 Note sungah phat ngawlna pan in, a heakkik peuma thupha pia tu in, Pathian in a Tapa Jesus thokiksak a, a masabel in note kungah hong sawl hi, ci hi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Peter le John Te Kiman  
\p
\v 1 Amate in mipite tungah thu a hil uh laitak in, thiampi te, biakinn lampui te le Sadducee te amate kungah hongpai uh hi,   
\p
\v 2 Sawltak te in mipi te thuhil a, Jesus tungtawn in thina pan thawkikna thu a pualak uh hu in, amate thinna in om tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Taciang amate in sawltak te man uh a, a zingciang dong thongtaksak uh hi: banghangziam cile tu in khua niam zo hi.   
\p
\v 4 Ahihang a thuhilna a zate in um uh hi; a umte a mimal in tul nga kiim pha uh hi.   
\s1 Peter in Israel Upa te Tung Thuson  
\p
\v 5 A zingciang in amate i lampui te, upa te le thukhamhil te,   
\p
\v 6 Taciang thiampi sang Annas le Caiaphas, John le Alexander, taciang thiampi sang i mealheak te theampo taw Jerusalem ah ki kaikhawm tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Amate a laizang ah dingsak uh a, bang thuneina, a hibale akua min taw in hibang te vawt nu ziam? ci dong hi.   
\p
\v 8 Tuazawkciang in Peter sia Thaa Thiangtho taw kidim a, amate tung ah, no mipi lampui te le Israel upa te,   
\p
\v 9 Tuni in hi cina pa tungah napha a ki vawtna le banghang in dam, ci thu taw kisai in thu hong dong nahi uh le;   
\p
\v 10 Note theampo le Israel mi theampo in he tavun, thinglamte tungah na khai uh a, Pathian in thina pan a thawkiksak Nazareth mi Jesus Christ min taw, note mai ah a ding pa sia dam hi.   
\p
\v 11 Noma inn sate in na nil uh hi suangtum sia inn khuampi suak hi.   
\p
\v 12 Ngupna sia mundang ah om ngawl hi; banghangziam cile ngupna i nga thei natu in vantung leinuai ah mindang a kipia om ngawl hi, ci hi.   
\s1 Jesus Min Taw Thuhil tu Kham  
\p
\v 13 Amate in Peter le John te hangsanna a mu uh ciang in, lai he ngawl le pilna nei ngawl te, ci he uh a, lamdangsa mama uh hi; taciang amate sia Jesus taw omkhawm ngei hi, ci zong he kik uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Taciang a damsak pa sia amate taw a dingkhawm nginge a mu uh hu in, tua thu langpan in bangma a pau thei bua uh hi.   
\p
\v 15 Amate thuneite kungpan pusuak tu in thu a piak zawk uh ciang, amate bek thu kikum khawm uh a,   
\p
\v 16 Hite banglaw tu hi ziam? banghangziam cile amate in a cepte tak nalamdang te vawt uh a, Jerusalem ah a om mi theampo mai ah vawt uh hi; taciang hi thu i nial thei bua hi.   
\p
\v 17 Ahihang hi thu mite sungah kizel thua ngawl tu in ahizong, kuama tungah hi min taw thuhil ngawl tu ahizong, nasiatak in thawmvau tawng, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 18 Taciang amate sam uh a, Jesus min taw thuhil ngawlhet tu le son nawn ngawl tu in thupia uh hi.   
\p
\v 19 Ahihang Peter le John in, Pathian thu sang in note i thu man tu sia Pathian mai ah a pha le a phangawl noma in khensat vun.   
\p
\v 20 Banghangziam cile ka mu uh thu le ka zak uh thu te son ngawl in ka om thei bua uh hi, ci in zo uh hi.   
\p
\v 21 Tua ahikom amate in a thawmvau zawk uh ciang in, bangbang in danpia tu ci a heak ngawl uh hu in suatak uh hi, banghangziam cile mi theampo in hi a sep uh te hang in Pathian minthang pok tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 22 Banghangziam cile hi cidamna nalamdang a tungah a kilangpa sia kum sawm li val zo hi.   
\s1 Hangsantak In Thungen  
\p
\v 23 A suatak zawk uh ciang, amate a lawmte kungah pai uh a, thiampi lian te le upa te in amate tungah a son theampo sonkik uh hi.   
\p
\v 24 Tua thu amate in a zak uh ciang in, thinkhat lung khat in Pathian kungah au tek uh a, Topa awng, Nangma sia van le lei, tuipi le a sung om theampo a vawt Pathian na hihi:   
\p
\v 25 Na naseam David tungtawn a son thu, banghang in Gentile mite thin-uk ziam, taciang mihing te banghang in matlap nei ngawl thu te ngaisun uh ziam?   
\p
\v 26 Leitung kumpi te ding uh a, taciang ngam uk te zong ki kaikhawm in Topa le Christ langpan uh hi.   
\p
\v 27 Banghangziam cile sathau na buaksa Nangma i a thiangtho nauno Jesus sia Herod le Pontius Pilate, Gentile mite le Israel mite taw, ki kaikhawm tek in, nasiatak in langpan uh hi,   
\p
\v 28 Banghangziam cile na khut taw na vawt tu te le na khensatsa ngaisutna te na khuangkhim natu a hihi.   
\p
\v 29 Tu in Topa awng, amate i hong thawmnvauna te en in: na sal te tungah na thu pualak tu in hangsanna hongpia tan,   
\p
\v 30 Na nauno thiangtho Jesus min taw cina te damsak tu le musakna te le nalamdang te vawt tu in na ban hong phal ta in, ci in thungen khawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 31 Amate thu a nget zawk uh ciang in, a kikhopna mun ling hi; taciang amate sia Tha Thiangtho taw kidim uh a, Pathian thu hangsantak in son uh hi.   
\s1 Na Theampo Neikhawm  
\p
\v 32 Taciang thu um mihonpi te thinkhat lungkhat taw in omkhawm tek uh hi: kuama in a neisa te uh keima a hi, ci ngawl uh hi; ahihang amate neisa na theampo neikhawm tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 33 Topa Jesus thawkikna thu ssawltak te in vangletna lianpi taw tettipang uh a: amate tungah hesuakna lianpi om hi.   
\p
\v 34 Amate sungah a ki tangsam khat zong a om bua uh hi: banghangziam cile lo ngam te, a hibale inn nei te in zuak uh hi, taciang a sum nga uh teng keng uh a,   
\p
\v 35 Sawltak te peang ah koi tek uh hi: taciang khatsim i kisapna bang in hawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 36 Taciang Joses, sawltak te in Barnabas a ci uh, Barnabas i a khiakna sia, henepna tapa a kici pa, ama sia Levi minam hi a, Cyprus ngam mi a hihi,   
\p
\v 37 Tua pa in a lo zuak a, a dangka keng in, sawltak te peang ah koi hi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Ananias le Sapphira  
\p
\v 1 Ahihang Ananias kici mi khat om a, a zi Sapphira taw a neisa uh zuak hi,   
\p
\v 2 Taciang a zi i heakpui nataw a man pawlkhat phualseal uh a, pawlkhat hong paipui in, sawltak te peang ah koi hi.   
\p
\v 3 Ahihang Peter in, Ananias awng, banghang in Tha Thiangtho theam tu in le lo man pawlkhat phualseal tu in Satan in na thinsung hong dimsak ziam?   
\p
\v 4 Lo a om lai in, nangma a hi ngawl ziam? taciang na zuak zawkciang zong, nangma thu ma hi ngawl ziam? banghang in na thinsung ah hibang ngaisun ni ziam? mihing theam hi ngawl in, Pathian theam hi zaw ni hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 5 Taciang Ananias in hi kammal te a zak ciang puk in, thi hi: hithu te a za theampo tungah launa lianpi hong theng hi.   
\p
\v 6 Taciang tangval te ding in, tuun uh hi, taciang puasang ah zawng in, vui uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Nai thum bang a kihal zawkciang in, bang thu piang ci zong he ngawl pi in a zi hong tum hi.   
\p
\v 8 Taciang Peter in a kungah, na lo uh hi za taw zuak nu ziam? hong son tan, ci dong hi. Taciang ama in, hi za ma hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 9 Tuazawkciang in Peter in ama kungah, bangbang in Topa Thaa ze-et tu in thukim thei nu ziam? en in, na pasal vui te i peang sia kongkha bul ah om hi, taciang amate in puasang ah hong zawng tu uh hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 10 Tua zawkpo ciang in Peter peang ah puksuk in, thi hi: taciang tangval te hong tum uh a, a thisa in mu uh hi, taciang, puasang ah zawng uh a, a pasal kungah vui uh hi.   
\p
\v 11 Taciang pawlpi le hi thu a za theampo tungah launa lianpi hong theng hi.   
\s1 Nalamdang Tampi Vawt  
\p
\v 12 Sawltakte i khut tungtawn in musakna le nalamdang tampi mite sungah vawt uh a; thu umte theampo Solomon buk sungah ki thukim tak in omtek uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Amate sia ngual in pok mama napi, a dang kuama in ki pawlpui ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 14 Taciang thu um mi numei le pasal mihonpi sia Topa kungah tam seseam ki belap hi.   
\p
\v 15 Cina te lamdung ah hong paipui uh a, Peter in a kantan laitak in, a lim in pawlkhat te lia tu in lupna le luppha te taw sial uh hi.   
\p
\v 16 Jerusalem kimkot khua tampi pan in mihonpi te zong hongpai uh a, cina te le doai te i zawthawk te zong hong paipui uh hi: taciang amate a vekpi in dam siat hi.   
\s1 Sawltakte Vawtsiat Thuak  
\p
\v 17 Tuazawkciang in thiampi sang le ama taw a om Sadducee te theampo thin-ukna taw dim in hong ding uh a,   
\p
\v 18 Sawltak te man in, thong sungah khia uh hi.   
\p
\v 19 Ahihang Topa vantungmi in zan ciang in thonginn kongkha te hong a, pusua siat hi,   
\p
\v 20 Taciang, pai vun a, ding in biakinn sung mipi te tungah hi nuntakna thu theampo son tavun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 21 Amate in hi thu a zak uh ciang in, zingtung in biakinn sungah tum uh a, thuhil uh hi. Ahihang thiampi sang le a naseam te hongpai uh a, thudokpi te le Israel upa te theampo sam hi, taciang amate in ngual sawl in sawltak te paipuisak hi.   
\p
\v 22 Ahihang palik te a thet ciang in, thong sungah a mu ngawl uh ciang, heakkik in son uh a,   
\p
\v 23 Thonginn phatak in a kikhak in mu khu hi, taciang thongcing te zong a puasang kongkha mai ah ding nginge hi: ahihang ka hon uh ciang in, a sungah mihing khat zong ka mu bua uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 24 Hi thu te thiampi sang, biakinn lampui te le thiampi lian te in a zak uh ciang in, bang thu hithong ziam, ci in lungmang mama uh hi.   
\p
\v 25 Tasia ciang in mi khat hongpai a, en vun, thong sung na khum mihing te biakinn sungah ding in mite thuhil san uh hi, ci son hi.   
\p
\v 26 Tuazawkciang in biakinn lampui le palik te pai hong pai uh a, amate zawthawk thu zang ngawl in paipui hi: banghangziam cile mite in suangtum taw a den tu a lau uh hang a hihi.   
\p
\v 27 Amate in sawltak te paipui uh a, thudokpi te mai ah dingsak uh hi: taciang thiampi sang in amate thu dong a,   
\p
\v 28 Hi min taw thuhil ngawl tu in nasiatak in thu hongpia zo hi ngawl khu ziam? taciang, en vun, Jerusalem sia note i hilna taw kidimsak siat zo nu hi, taciang hisia pa thisan sia kote tungah hong thengsak nuam nu hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 29 Taciang Peter le a dang sawltak te in zo kik uh a, mihing te thu sang in Pathian thu ka zui zaw tu uh hi.   
\p
\v 30 Note in thing tungah that in, na khai uh Jesus sia ka pu le pa te i Pathian in thokiksak hi.   
\p
\v 31 Israel te maw kisikik na le maw maisakna pia tu in Ama sia Pathian in a ziatsang khut taw To le Ngumpa in lamsang zo hi.   
\p
\v 32 Taciang kote sia hi thu te i tetti te ka hi uh hi; taciang Pathian in a thu a zui te tungah a piak Tha Thiangtho zong tetti a hihi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 33 Amate in tua thu a zak uh ciang in, nasiatak in a thin uh uk a, sawltak te that tu in ngaisun uh hi.   
\p
\v 34 Tuazawkciang in thudokpi te sung pan Pharisee khat, Gamaliel a kici, thukham taw kisai doctor a hi, mi theampo sungah a ki zakta pa in, sawltak te tawmvei sung pusuaksak tu in thupia a;   
\p
\v 35 Amate tung ah, no Israel mite, hi thu taw kisai in na vawt tu uh thu kidawm vun.   
\p
\v 36 Banghangziam cile hi te om ma in Theudas a kici khat piang ngei a, ama le ama sia mi thupi khat bang in ki suangtak mama hi; mihing zali kiim in beal phot napi, ama ki that hi; taciang a thu zuite theampo ki thethang siat a, bokik siat hi.   
\p
\v 37 Hisia pa om ma in Galilee mi, Judas kici misim hun laitak in hong piang leleau a, a nungzui mi tamma kaizawn hi: ama zong bokik veve a; a thuzui te theampo a vekpi in, ki thethang leleau hi.   
\p
\v 38 Taciang tu in kong son hi, hi te pial vun a, amate om in om lel tahen: banghangziam cile hi ngaisutna, a hibale, hi nasep sia mihing tung pan ahile, bokik siat lel tu hi:   
\p
\v 39 Ahihang, hisia sia Pathian kung pan ahile, na zozo batu uh hi; Pathian langpan in a do zong na suak thei zawsap tu uh hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 40 Amate in Gamaliel i son thu lungkim tek uh hi: taciang sawltak te sam uh a, a sat zawkciang in, Jesus min taw thuhil nawn ngawl tu in thupia a, suatak uh hi.   
\p
\v 41 Taciang amte Jesus min hang in maizumna thuaktak in a cepte hu in angtang mama in thudokpi te mai pan pusuak uh hi.   
\p
\v 42 Taciang nisim in biakinn sung le inn tatuam ah tatsat ngawl in Jesus Christ thuhil in pualak tek uh hi.   
\c 6  
\s1 A Masabel Upa Sali Te  
\p
\v 1 Tua hun sung, nungzui te hong khan ciang in, Greek te in Hebrew te langpan in kamtam na hong piang hi, banghangziam cile Greek meingong te sia nisim an a hawm uh ciang in ki ngaingonsak hi.   
\p
\v 2 Tua zawkciang in sawltak sawm le ni te in nungzui mihonpi te amate kungah sam a, kote Pathian thu nusia in an ka hawm tu uh sia lungkim huai ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 3 Tua ahikom, suapui te awng, noma sung pan in a belcing minpha, Tha Thiangtho le ciimna taw a kidim mi sali hong zong tavun a, hi nasep amate i ap tu hi.   
\p
\v 4 Ahihang kote thungen le Pathian thu sungah a tawntung in ka kipumpiak tu uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Taciang amate sonbang in mihonpi theampo lungkim uh a: amate in, upna le Tha Thiangtho taw a kidim Stephen, Philip, Prochorus, Nicanor, Timon, Parmenas le Antioch khua mi Judah biakna ah a tum Nicolas te teal uh hi.   
\p
\v 6 Amate sia sawltak te mai ah dingsak uh a, thu a ngetsak uh ciang in, amate lutung ah a khut nga uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang Pathian thu hong khang a; Jerusalem ah nungzui te nasiatak in hong ki belap hi; taciang thiampi tampi te in upna thu zui uh hi.   
\s1 Stephen Ki Matna Thu  
\p
\v 8 Taciang upna le vangletna taw a kidim Stephen in, mite sungah a lian mama nalamdang le lim tumdang lianpi te vawt hi.   
\p
\v 9 Tuazawkciang in A Suaktate synagogue a kici, synagogue sungah Cyrene mite, Alexandria mite, Cilicia mite le Asia mite Stephen taw thu kinial uh hi.   
\p
\v 10 Amate in Stephen i ciimna le thaa taw a pauna te a nalh zo bua uh hi.   
\p
\v 11 Tuazawkciang in amate in mite sumnguk pia ku uh a, tua te in, hisia pa in Moses le Pathian langpan in mindaisak na kammal te a pau sia kote in ka za uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 12 Taciang amate in mihonpi te, upa te le thukhamhil te hol uh a, Stephen kungah hongpai uh hi, taciang thudokpi te kungah paipui uh a,   
\p
\v 13 Hisia pa in mun thiangtho le thukham langpan in mindaisak na kammal te tatsat ngawl in pau hi, ci uh hi, tabang in leilot tetti tampi koi uh hi:   
\p
\v 14 Banghangziam cile, Nazareth mi Jesus in hi mun susia tu a, Moses i hongpiak thukham te lai tu hi, ci in hisia pa in a son ka za uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 15 Thudokpi te thukhen na mun ah a to theampo in, Stephen sia phatak in sal uh a, a maitang sia vantungmi te maitang bang in mu uh hi.   
\c 7  
\s1 Stephen Thusonna  
\p
\v 1 Tuazawkciang in thiampi sang in, hi thu te tabangma ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 2 Taciang Stephen in, suapui te le pa te awng, ngai vun; i pa Abraham sia Haran ah a om ma, Mesopotamia ah a omlai tak in, a vanglian Pathian ama tungah kilang a,   
\p
\v 3 Ama tung ah, na ngam le na mipui te sung pan in pusuak in a, kong lak tu ngam ah pai in, ci hi.   
\p
\v 4 Tuazawkciang in Chaldaeans ngam pan pusuak a, Haran khua ah om hi: tua mun pan a pa a thi ciang in, tu in na omna uh mun, hi ngamsung ah ki khin hi.   
\p
\v 5 Taciang hi ngam sungah a peang ngak natu na ngawn, mun pia ngawl hi: ahihang ama le a suan le pal te hi ngam pia tu in ta a nei ma in, kamciam pia zo hi.   
\p
\v 6 Taciang Pathian in hi bang in son hi, a suan le pal te ngamdang ah peam tu uh a; kum zali sung sal tang in ngimna thuak tu uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang a saltanna mun minam te keima in thu ka khen tu hi, tua zawkciang in amate pusuak tu uh a, hi mun ah keima na seam tu uh hi, ci in Pathian in ci hi.   
\p
\v 8 Taciang Pathian in Abraham sia vunteap tanna kamciam pia hi: taciang Abraham in Isaac nei a, ni liat ni ciang in a vunteap tansak hi; taciang Isaac in Jacob nei a; taciang Jacob in minam makai sawm le ni te nei hi.   
\p
\v 9 Taciang minam makai te in ki enna hang in Joseph sia Egypt ngam ah zuak uh hi napi: Pathian in ompui a,   
\p
\v 10 Haksatna theampo sung pan suatak in, Egypt kumpipa Pharaoh mai ah ciimna le maipha pia hi; taciang Egypt ngam le ama inn theampo tungah a uk tu in vawt hi.   
\p
\v 11 Egypt ngam le Canaan ngamsung theampo ah kialtung a, taciang haksatna lianpi theng ahikom in i pu i pa te bangma neak tu muzo ngawl uh hi.   
\p
\v 12 Ahihang Jacob in Egypt ngam ah an om hi, ci a zak ciang in, i pu le pa te a masabel in paisak hi.   
\p
\v 13 Taciang a ni veina ciang in Joseph in a suapui te kungah ama thu hesak hi; taciang Joseph i mealheak te Pharaoh kungah hesak hi.   
\p
\v 14 Tuazawkciang Joseph in paisak a, a pa Jacob le a mealheak theampo mihing sawm sali le nga te ama kungah sam hi.   
\p
\v 15 Tua ahikom Jacob sia Egypt ngam ah pai a, ama le i pupi te tuak ah thi hi,   
\p
\v 16 A luanghawm sia Shechem ah pua uh a, Abraham in Hamor tapa kung pan dangka taw a lei sa than ah vui hi. Hamor sia Shechem i pa a hihi.   
\p
\v 17 Ahihang Pathian i Abraham tung kiciamna taw a kamciamna hun hong nai ciang in, Egypt ngam ah amate khang in pung seseam uh hi,   
\p
\v 18 Joseph a he ngawl a dang kumpi khat hong khan dong in pung uh hi.   
\p
\v 19 Tua kumpipa in i mipui te philphit tak in theambawl uh a, nausen te a nungta ngawl tu in vawk tu in i pupi te sia phatngawlna taw vawtsia uh hi.   
\p
\v 20 Tua hun in Moses suak a, ama sia hoi mama hi, taciang a pa inn ah tha thum sung ki vak hi:   
\p
\v 21 Taciang ama sia a puasang ah a ki vawk ciang in, Pharaoh tanu in la a, ama tapa tu in vak hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tua Moses in Egypt te pilna theampo sin a, ama sia kampau le sepna ah lawcing mama hi.   
\p
\v 23 Taciang ama sia kum sawmli a phak ciang in, a suapui Israel tate ve nopna a thinsung pan hong suak hi.   
\p
\v 24 Israel mi khat a man ngawl in a thuak a mu ciang in, tua pa ngum a, a vawtsia Egypt pa sia phulam in that hi:   
\p
\v 25 Banghangziam cile Pathian in ama khut zang in amate suatak tu hi, ci a suapui te in he tu in ngaisun hi:   
\p
\v 26 A zingciang in Israel mi ni a kihau te kungah pai a, leptua sawm in, note u nau nu hi; banghang in kihau nu ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 27 Ahihang a innpam pa a vawtsia pa in Moses sawn a, nang akua in kote tungah thunei le thukhen tu in hong vawt ziam?   
\p
\v 28 Zei ni Egypt pa na thalup bang in hong that nuam ni ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 29 Tuazawkciang hisia pa i kampau hang in Moses tai a Midian ngam ah peamta in om hi, tua mun ah tapa ni nei hi.   
\p
\v 30 Kum sawm li a bo ciang in, Sinai mual duisung ah Topa vantungmi sia lophung kuang bang in kilang hi.   
\p
\v 31 Tasia Moses in a mu ciang in, a mu thu lamdangsa hi: en tu in a neak ciang in, Topa aw ama tungah theng a,   
\p
\v 32 Keima sia na pu le pa te i Pathian, Abraham Pathian, Isaac Pathian le Jacob Pathian ka hihi, ci hi. Tuazawkciang in Moses sia ling a, en zong en ngam ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 33 Tuazawkciang in Topa in ama kungah, na peangdap sut in: banghangziam cile na dinna mun sia a thiangtho leitang a hihi.   
\p
\v 34 Keima in ka mu zo hi, Egypt ngam ah ka mite haksatna keima in mu zo khi hi, taciang amate tauna ka za zo a, suatak tu in kong tuaksuk hi. Taciang tu in hongpai tan, Egypt ngam ah hong sawl tu khi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 35 Hi Moses sia amate in nial uh a, nangma sia hong uk tu le thukhen tu in a kua in hong vawt ziam? ci uh hi. Pathian in Moses sia lophung sung pan ama tungah a kilang vantungmi i khut tungtawn in ukpa le ngumpa tu in paisak hi.   
\p
\v 36 Moses in amate pusua pui a, tua zawkciang in Egypt ngam, san tuipi le senneal ngam sungah kum sawmli sung, nalamdang le musakna tampi te lak hi.   
\p
\v 37 Topa na Pathian in keima bang kamsang khat, na suapui te sung pan ka piangsak tu hi; note in a thu na ngai tu uh hi, tabang in Israel tate tungah a sonpa sia Moses a hihi.   
\p
\v 38 Ama sia senneal ngamsung a om pawlpi te kungah ahizong, Sinai mual ah vantungmi taw a ki paupui na ah ahizong, taciang i pu i pa te taw ahizong, omkhawm ngei a: ama sia eite tungah hongpiak tu a nungta kammal te a sang pa a hihi:   
\p
\v 39 I pu i pa te in thu ni ngawl uh a, amate kung pan sawnthal uh hi, taciang amate thinsung pan in Egypt ngam ah heakkik uh hi,   
\p
\v 40 Amate in Aaron tung ah, kote i mai ah a pai tu in pathian te hong vawtsak tan: banghangziam cile Egypt ngam pan hong pusua hi Moses sia bangsuak, ci ka he bua uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 41 Taciang tua hun sung in amate in khuino vawt uh a, milim tungah biakpiakna pia uh hi, taciang amate khut taw a vawttawm nate tungah lungdam in om uh hi.   
\p
\v 42 Tuazawkciang in Pathian in amate nungngat a, van aksi te bia tu in koicip hi; kamsang te laibu sungah a ki atsa bang in, Maw, no Israel minam te, senneal ngam ah kum sawm li sung a ki thatlum ngamsa te le biakpiakna te nong pia uh ziam?   
\p
\v 43 Note in Molech i biakbuk le na aksi pathian Remphan, na biak tu in na vawttawm uh milim te na keng uh hi: tua ahikom keima in note Babylon ngalkhat dong in kong paipui tu hi.   
\p
\v 44 I pu le pa te in senneal ngam sungah biakbuk tetti te nei hi, Moses tung son uh a, a mu uh lim bang in, vawt tu in sawl uh hi.   
\p
\v 45 Tuazawkciang in i pu le pa te in tua biakbuk sia Gentile te i neisa ngamsung ah Joshua taw tumpui uh hi, tua Gentile te sia Pathian in David hun dong i pu le pa te mai pan in hawlkhia siat hi.   
\p
\v 46 David in Pathian mai ah maipha nga a, Jacob Pathian atu biakbuk sa tu in ngen hi.   
\p
\v 47 Ahihang Solomon in Pathian atu in inn sa hi.   
\p
\v 48 Ahihang a sangbel Pathian sia khut taw a kisa biakinn sungah om ngawl hi; kamsang i a son na ah,   
\p
\v 49 Vantung sia ka kumpi tokhum hi a, leitung sia ka peang ngakna hi, bangbang inn kei atu satu nu ziam? a hibale ka tawlngak na mun sia bang ziam?   
\p
\v 50 Hi nate theampo sia keima khut taw ka vawt hi ngawl ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 51 Note ngawng ngu khoh te le thinsung le nakheng vunteap tan ngawl te awng, note in Tha Thiangtho na khak tawntung uh hi; na pu le pa te i a vawt uh bang in note in zong na vawt uh hi.   
\p
\v 52 Kamsang te sung pan na pu le pa te in a vawtsiat ngawl khat beak a om ziam? Mi thutang pa hongpai natu thu a pualak te amate in that uh a; tu in note sia tua mi thutang pa a zuak te le a that te na hi uh hi:   
\p
\v 53 Vantungmi te i huna taw thukham na sang uh a, na zui bua uh hi, ci hi.   
\s1 Stephen Suangtum taw Sep  
\p
\v 54 Amate in hi thu te a zak uh ciang in, nasiatak in thin-uk mama uh a, a ha te ngoai uh hi.   
\p
\v 55 Ahihang Stephen sia Tha Thiangtho taw kidim in, vantung lam tangtak in ento hi, taciang Pathian vangletna le Jesus sia Pathian ziatsang ah a ding mu hi.   
\p
\v 56 En vun, van ki hong a, Pathian ziatsang ah mihing Tapa a ding ka mu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 57 Tuazawkciang in aw ngingtak in au uh a, a bil uh hum in, ki lomtang in Stephen sangah hong tai uh hi,   
\p
\v 58 Taciang khuapua ah nawt uh a, suangtum taw deang uh hi: taciang tetti te in a nik le puan te tangvalpa peang ah koi uh hi, tua tangvalpa min sia Saul a hihi.   
\p
\v 59 Amate in Stephen sia suangtum taw deang uh hi, taciang Stephen in, Pathian sam a, Topa Jesus awng, ka tha hong sang tan, ci hi.   
\p
\v 60 Taciang ama khupdin in, Topa awng, hi mawna sia amate tungah koi heak in, ci in a ngingtak in au hi, tabang a au zawkciang in ama mutthip hi.   
\c 8  
\s1 Saul in Pawlpi Vawtsia  
\p
\v 1 Taciang Stephen i thina ah Saul a lungkim hi. Tua hun sung in Jerusalem pawlpi langpan in vawtsiatna lianpi om hi; sawltak te simngawl, thu um mite theampo sia Judah ngam le Samaria ngam muntheampo ah peakkeak uh hi.   
\p
\v 2 Stephen sia biakna sang a kipia mite in zawng in vui uh hi, taciang nasiatak in kaa uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Saul ahile, inn sim ah tum a, numei pasal ci ngawl in kaikeak a, taciang thonginn ah ap in, pawlpi susia hi.   
\s1 Samaria ah Philip  
\p
\v 4 Tua ahikom mun theampo ah a ki thethang te mun tatuam ah pai in Pathian thu tangko tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Tuazawkciang in Philip sia Samaria khuapi ah pai a, amate tungah Christ thuhil hi.   
\p
\v 6 Taciang Philip in nalamdang te a vawtna za uh a, a mu uh hu in a thuhil nate mite in kilomtang in phatak in ngai uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Banghangziam cile doai te nangawn in au in, amate i thin-apsak mihing te sung pan pusuak uh hi: taciang pumzaw te le peangbai te zong damsak hi.   
\p
\v 8 Taciang tua khuapi sungah lungdamna lianpi om hi.   
\s1 Bum Thiam Simon  
\p
\v 9 Ahihang tua mun ah Simon a kici mi khat om a, ama sia nidang in tua khuapi sungah bum le ai zang in Samaria mite bum a, ama le ama mi thupi khat in ki son hi.   
\p
\v 10 Mi theampo, a nobel pan a lianbel dong in a thu phatak in ni uh a, hisia pa sia Pathian vangletna lianpi hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 11 Hun saupi sung bum le ai taw ngual a bum hu in, ngual in ama zakta uh hi.   
\p
\v 12 Ahihang Philip in Pathian kumpingam le Jesus Christ min taw kisai thu te a hil ciang in, numei zong pasal zong tui ki phum uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Tuazawkciang in Simon ama tatak zong in um hi: taciang tui a ki phum zawkciang in, Philip taw ki thawl hi, taciang nalamdang le musakna a kivawtte lamdangsa mama in en hi.   
\p
\v 14 Tu in Jerusalem a om sawltak te in Samaria mite in Pathian thu sang zo uh hi, ci a zak uh ciang in Peter le John sia amate kungah paisak uh a:   
\p
\v 15 Amate a thet uh ciang in, Tha Thiangtho a nga thei natu in thungetsak hi:   
\p
\v 16 (Banghangziam cile Tha Thiangtho sia kuama tungah theng ngawl lai hi: Topa Jesus min taw tui ki phum bek sang pheang uh hi.)   
\p
\v 17 Tuazawkciang in Peter le John in amate tungah a khut te nga uh hi, taciang amate in Tha Thiangtho sang uh uh.   
\p
\v 18 Taciang sawltak te in khutngakna tungtawn in Tha Thiangtho piakna sia Simon in a mu ciang in, sawltak te dangka pia a,   
\p
\v 19 Akuapo tungah khut ka nga ahizong Tha Thiangtho a san thei natu in, hi vangletna kei zong hong pia tavun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 20 Ahihang Peter in ama tung ah, na dangka sia nangma taw lalcip tahen, banghangziam cile nangma in Pathian letsong sia dangka taw lei thei tu in na ngaisun hi.   
\p
\v 21 Nangma sia hi thu taw kisaina na nei bua hi: banghangziam cile Pathian mai ah na thinsung phangawl hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tua ahikom hina phatngawlna pan in kisik in a, Pathian kungah thungen in, tabang hile na thinsung ngaisutna mawna hong maisak tu hi.   
\p
\v 23 Banghangziam cile nangma sia a kha mama thinkha sungah na om a, phatngawlna in hong hencip hi, ci ka he hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 24 Tuazawkciang in Simon in, na son thu te theampo khat zong ka tungah hong thet ngawl natu in, Topa tungah thu hong ngetsak tavun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 25 Taciang amate in Topa thuhil le tetti a pan zawk uh ciang Jerusalem ah heakkik uh a, Samaria mite khua tampi ah lungdamna thuhil uh hi.   
\s1 Philip le Ethiopia Mangpa  
\p
\v 26 Taciang Topa vantungmi in Philip tung ah, ding in a, Jerusalem pan thangsang Gaza paina lampi ah paisuk in, tua mun sia senneal ngam a hihi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 27 Taciang Philip ding in pai hi: taciang, en in, Ethiopa mi cil ki nget khat, Ethiopia kumpinu Candace khut nuai ah za lian mama le neisa theampo a keampa sia Jerusalem ah Pathian bia tu in hongpai a,   
\p
\v 28 Ama sia a ciakik lam in, siphu leang to in kamsang Isaiah laibu sim hi.   
\p
\v 29 Thaa in Philip tung ah, neakphei in a, hi siphu leang tungah ama taw paikhawm vun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 30 Philip sia tua pa kungah tai a, kamsang Isaiah laibu a sim za hi, taciang na sim sia na tel ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 31 Tua pa in, mi khatpo in hong hil bua ahile, bangbang in tel thei tu khi ziam? ci hi. Taciang ama in Philip sia siphu leang tungah kato in ama taw tokhawm tu in sam hi.   
\p
\v 32 Laithiangtho a sim na mun sia, Ama sia ngaw tu in a ki paipui tuu bang a hihi; taciang a mulmet pa mai ah a ham ngawl tuuno bang in, Ama sia a kam zong ka ngawl hi:   
\p
\v 33 Ki zawnsak na sungah a man ngawl in thukhenna thuak hi: taciang akua in ama suan te tungah tangko tu ziam? banghangziam cile ama nuntakna sia hi leitung pan in la uh hi, a ci na mun a hihi.   
\p
\v 34 Taciang tua cil ki nget pa in Philip zo kik a, kong thum hi, hong son tan, kamsang in akua thu son ziam? ama thu ziam, a hibale midang thu son ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 35 Tuazawkciang in Philip in a kam hong a, tua laithiangtho pan kipan in, Jesus thu dong ama tungah hil hi.   
\p
\v 36 Tabang in amate lampi dung ah a pai uh laitak in, tui omna mun ah theng uh hi: tua cil ki nget pa in, en in, hi mun ah tui om hi; tui ki phum tu bang in hong khak ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 37 Taciang Philip in, na thinsung theampo taw na um le, ki phum thei ni hi, ci hi. Taciang ama in, Jesus Christ sia Pathian Tapa hi, ci ka um hi, ci in zo hi.   
\p
\v 38 Ama in siphu leang tawlnga tu in thupia hi: taciang a ni in tuisung ah tuaksuk uh a, Philip in ama tuiphumna pia hi.   
\p
\v 39 Taciang amate tui sung pan a pusua uh ciang in, Topa Thaa in Philip lato a, tua pa in mu kik nawn ngawl hi: taciang lungdamtak in a lampi dung ah paisuak hi.   
\p
\v 40 Ahihang Philip sia Azotus khua ah, mite in mu uh hi: Caesarea a thet dong khuapi theampo ah Pathian thuhil hi.   
\c 9  
\s1 Saul Ki Khealna  
\r Sawl. 22:4-16; 26:9-18  
\p
\v 1 Taciang Saul in Topa nungzui te that tu in nasiatak in thawmvau tawntung lai a, thiampi sang pa kungah pai in,   
\p
\v 2 Ama tung pan in, Damascus synagogue te tung piak tu lai te ngen hi, tua mun ah Topa lampi\f + \fr 9:2 \fq Lampi \ft Tua hun thu umte a cinopna hi\f* zui te a mu le, numei pasal ci ngawl, hen in Jerusalem ah paipui sawm hi.   
\p
\v 3 Ama a khualhaw na, Damascus hong theng dektak hi: taciang thakhatthu in van pan khuavak in a kimkot teng tan hi:   
\p
\v 4 Ama sia lei ah pusuk a, \wj Saul, Saul, banghang hong vawtsia ni ziam?\wj* ci aw za hi.   
\p
\v 5 Saul in, Topa awng, akua ni ziam? ci hi. Taciang Topa in, \wj Keima sia na vawtsiat Jesus khi hi: nangma atu in a zum khat sui sia thuakhak mama hi, \wj* ci hi.   
\p
\v 6 Taciang ama ling va dil le laukawm in, Topa awng, bang hong vawtsak nuam ni ziam? ci hi. Taciang Topa in ama tung ah, \wj Ding in a, khuapi sungah pai in, taciang na vawt hamtang tu thu kong son tu hi, \wj* ci hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang ama taw khualhaw te in aw nging za uh hinapi, mihing khat zong mu ngawl uh a hikom kamkhat zong pau ngawl in ding uh hi.   
\p
\v 8 Saul sia lei pan tho to a; a mit a ha ciang in, mihing kuama mu ngawl hi: ahihang amate in a khut pan kai a, Damascus khua sungah paipui uh hi.   
\p
\v 9 Taciang ni thum sung khua mu ngawl a, an ne ngawl in tui zong dawn ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 10 Damascus khuasung ah Ananias a kici nungzui khat om hi; taciang Topa in mangmuna sung pan in ama kungah, \wj Ananias awng, \wj* ci hi. Taciang ama in, en in, Topa awng, keima hiak ah ka om hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 11 Topa in ama tung ah, \wj Ding in a, a Tang, a kici lampi ah pai tan, taciang Judah inn ah Tarsus khuami, Saul a kici mi khat zong in: banghangziam cile, en in, ama thungen in om hi, \wj*   
\p
\v 12 \wj Taciang ama in Ananias a kici mi khat tum a, khua a mu thei natu in, ama tungah a khut a ngak sia mangmuna sungah mu zo hi, \wj* ci hi.   
\p
\v 13 Ananias in, Topa awng, Jerusalem ah na mithiangtho te kungah phat ngawlna a vawt bangza in tam ci, hisia pa thu mi tampi te tung pan in ka za zo hi:   
\p
\v 14 Taciang na min hong sam theampo hen tu in thiampi lian te tung pan thuneina nei hi, ci in zo hi.   
\p
\v 15 Ahihang Topa in Ananias tung ah, \wj Pai in, banghangziam cile ama sia keima atu in a kiteal beal hi a, Gentile mite, kumpi te le Israel tate mai ah ka min a pua tu pa a hihi:\wj*   
\p
\v 16 \wj Banghangziam cile keima in ama sia ka min hang in a thuak hamtang tu te bangza in lian ziam, ci sia ka lak tu hi, \wj* ci hi.   
\p
\v 17 Taciang Ananias pai a, inn sungah tum hi; Saul tungah a khut nga a, suapui pa Saul awng, khua mu in, Tha Thiangtho taw na dim thei natu, nong pai na lampi, na tungah hong kilang Topa Jesus in hong sawl hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 18 Tasia pociang in Saul i mit pan in ngasalip a kibang khat tak hi: taciang thakhatthu in khuamu hi, taciang ding a, tui ki phum hi.   
\s1 Paul in Damascus ah Thuhil  
\p
\v 19 Saul sia an a neak zawkciang in, a thadim hi. Tuazawkciang in Damascus ah nungzui te taw ni tampi sung omkhawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 20 Tua zawkpo ciang synagogue sungah Christ sia Pathian Tapa hi, ci in thuhil hi.   
\p
\v 21 Ahihang a zate theampo in lamdangsa mama uh a, ama sia Jerusalem ah Jesus min a lo te theampo a susia pa hi ngawl ziam, amate a hen zawkciang, thiampi lian te kungah a paipui nop hang hi ngawl ziam? ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 22 Ahihang Saul sia thahat seseam a, Jesus in Christ a hihi, ci a pualak hu in, Damascus a om Judah mite buaisak mama hi.   
\p
\v 23 Ni tampi a cin zawkciang in, Judah mite in ama that tu in kikum khawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 24 Ahihang amate i pan hunlam Saul in he hi. Taciang amate in Saul that tu in kongpi te sun taw zan taw cing uh hi.   
\p
\v 25 Tuazawkciang in nungzui te in Saul sia zan in paipui uh a, bawm taw luphung pan in khiasuk uh hi.   
\s1 Paul in Jerusalem ah Thuhil  
\p
\v 26 Saul sia Jerusalem a thet ciang in, nungzui te taw kikop sawm hi: ahihang amate in Saul sia nungzui hi, ci um ngawl in lau uh hi.   
\p
\v 27 Ahihang Barnabas in panpui a, sawltak te kungah paipui hi, taciang lampi ah ama in Topa mu a, Topa zong in ama paupui hi, ci le, Damascus ah Jesus min taw hangsantak in Pathian thuhil hi, ci amate tungah tangko hi.   
\p
\v 28 Taciang Saul sia Jerusalem ah amate taw sungtum le pusuak in omtek uh hi.   
\p
\v 29 Taciang Topa Jesus min taw hangsantak in thuhil a, Greek mite taw ki nial uhhi: tua ahikom amate in Saul that nuam uh hi.   
\p
\v 30 Tua thu suapui te in a heak uh ciang in, Caesaria ah paipui uh a, Tarsus ah puak uh hi.   
\p
\v 31 Tuazawkciang in Judah ngam, Galilee ngam le Samaria ngam theampo ah pawlpi te thinnopna taw kiptak in om uh hi; taciang Topa zatakna le Tha Thiangtho henepna sungah nungta in, khangto uh hi.   
\s1 Aeneas Dam  
\p
\v 32 Peter sia mun tatuam ah khualhaw a, Lydda khua a om mithiangtho te kung theng hi.   
\p
\v 33 Tua mun ah Aeneas a kici khat taw ki mu hi, ama sia a pumzaw a, lupmun tungah kum liat sung tho thei ngawl in lum hi.   
\p
\v 34 Peter in ama tung ah, Aeneas awng, Jesus Christ in hong damsak hi: tho in a, na lupna zial in, ci hi. Tasia pociang in tho hi.   
\p
\v 35 Taciang Lydda le Sharon ah a om theampo in mu uh a, Topa sangah heakkik uh hi.   
\s1 Dorcas Thina le Thawkikna  
\p
\v 36 Tu in Joppa khua ah Tabitha a kici nungzui khat om hi. Tabitha a khiakna sia Dorcas a cinopna a hihi: hi numei in na pha tampi vawt a, mizawng tampi hu hi.   
\p
\v 37 Tua ni in, ama sia a cina in thi hi: taciang amate in a luang a sil zawk uh ciang, inn tung doituam ah sial uh hi.   
\p
\v 38 Lydda sia Joppa taw kinai ahikom in nungzui te in Peter tua mun ah om hi, ci za uh a, manlangtak in hongpai natu in, mihing sawl in sam uh hi.   
\p
\v 39 Taciang Peter ding in amate taw pai hi. A thet uh ciang in Peter sia inntung doituam ah paipui uh hi: tua mun ah meingong te theampo a hui ah ding in kap lialua uh a, a nuntaklai a ta laktong le puan te zong lak hi.   
\p
\v 40 Peter in amate pusuaksak siat a, khupdin in thu a nget zawkciang, a luang sangah kihei in, Tabitha, tho in, ci hi. Taciang a mit hong hak hi: Peter a mu ciang in, to hi.   
\p
\v 41 Peter in a khut thak in kaito a, mithiangtho te le meingong te a sap zawkciang in, a nungta in ap hi.   
\p
\v 42 Tua thu sia Joppa khua sung theampo ah thang a; mi tampi in Topa um uh hi.   
\p
\v 43 Peter sia Joppa khua ah savun vawtpa Simon kungah ni tampi sung om hi.   
\c 10  
\s1 Cornelius in Peter Sam  
\p
\v 1 Caesarea khua ah Cornelius a kici khat om hi, ama sia Italy ngalkap hon, a kici ngalkap zakhat uk ngalkapmang a hihi,   
\p
\v 2 Ama sia biakna sangah a kipia, a innkuan bup taw Pathian zakta khat, mizawng te huna tampi a pia, tatsat ngawl in Pathian tungah thu a ngen pa a hihi.   
\p
\v 3 Nitak nai thum kiim pawl in a thiangtak in a mangmuna sungah, Pathian vantungmi khat a kungah hongpai a, Cornelius, ci in sam hi.   
\p
\v 4 Tua vantungmi laukawm in en a, bang thu ziam, Topa? ci hi. Vantungmi in, na thungetna te le mizawngte na hu nate Pathian mai ah theng a, Pathian in hong ciamte hi.   
\p
\v 5 Tu in mihing pawlkhat Joppa ah paisak in, Simon Peter kici pa samsak tan.   
\p
\v 6 Ama sia tuipi hui ah a teang savun vawt Simon inn ah zintung hi: hi Simon inn sia tuihui ah om a, ama in na vawt tu a kilawm te hong son tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 7 Cornelius a paupui vantungmi a heakkik zawkciang in, a naseam ni le biakna sang ki pia a, tatsat ngawl in ama a cing ngalkap khat sam hi;   
\p
\v 8 Hi thu te theampo a son zawkciang in, Joppa ah paisak hi.   
\s1 Peter in Mangmu  
\p
\v 9 A zingciang in, amate khual a haw uh laitak, Joppa a thet dektak uh ciang, Peter sia sun nai sawmleni kiim pawl in, inn tungah thungen tu in kato hi:   
\p
\v 10 Peter sia a ngil hong kial mama a, an ne nuam zo hi: ahihang amate i an neak tu a vawt laitak in mangmu hi.   
\p
\v 11 Van kihong a, puan a ki pheak kingli nei a lian mama na koina taw akibang khat leitung ama kungah hong ki khiasuk mu hi:   
\p
\v 12 A sungah peang li nei nganhing a tatuam, sapi te, a bokvak te le van a leang vacim te om hi.   
\p
\v 13 Aw khat in ama tung ah, Peter awng; tho in, ngo in a, ne in, ci hi.   
\p
\v 14 Ahihang Peter in, hi ngawl hi, Topa awng; banghangziam cile a nin le a thiangtho ngawl te ne ngei ngawl khi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 15 Pathian in a thianthosak te nin hi ci heak in, taciang tua aw in a nivei na son thua hi.   
\p
\v 16 Hisia thumvei dong tabang in vawt hi: taciang tua na koina sia van ah ki lato kik hi.   
\p
\v 17 Peter in hi mangmuna a mu sia a khiakna a lungman laitak in, en vun, Cornelius kung pan a kisawlte Simon inn zong in kongbiang mai ah ding uh hi.   
\p
\v 18 Taciang a sap zawkciang in, Peter a kici Simon sia hiak ah hong tung ziam, ci in dong uh hi.   
\p
\v 19 Peter in tua mangmuna thu a ngaisut laitak in, Thaa in, en in, mihing thum in nang hong zong hi.   
\p
\v 20 Tua ahikom tho in a, tuaksuk in, bangma lungmang heak in, banghangziam cile amate sia keima i sawl a hihi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 21 Tuazawkciang in Peter sia Cornelius i sawl te kungah tuaksuk a, en vun, na zon uh sia keima khi hi: banghang in hongpai nu ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 22 Amate in, ngalkap zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa, mi thutang, Pathian a zakta le Judah minam theampo sungah minpha, Cornelius in Pathian kung pan kidop piakna thu theng a, a thiangtho vantungmi in ama inn ah nangma hongsawl hi, taciang namgma thuhil ngai tu hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 23 Tuazawkciang in Peter in amate innsung ah sam a, amate zan taam uh hi. A zingciang in Peter sia amate taw pai khawm a, Joppa ah suapui te in zong zui uh hi.   
\s1 Peter Cornelius Inn Theng  
\p
\v 24 A zingciang in amate sia Caesarea ah tum uh hi. Taciang Cornelius in a mealheak te le a lawmte kaikhawm khol in ngak tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 25 Peter a tum ciang in, Cornelius in muak a, a peang ah kun in bia hi.   
\p
\v 26 Ahihang Peter in ama kaito a, ding in; keima zong mihing ma khi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 27 Peter in a paupui kawm in innsung ah tum uh a, a pai tam mama mu hi.   
\p
\v 28 Peter in amate tung ah, Judah mi khat mi namdang te taw ki thawl tu, a hibale, a kungah pai tu sia ngeina om ngawl hi, ci na he tek uh hi; ahihang khatpo sia a nin, a hibale, a thiangtho ngawl, a kici ngawl natu in Pathian in hong lak zo hi.   
\p
\v 29 Tua ahikom note kungah hong sawl pociang, nial ngawl in kongpai hi: tua ahikom bang deina in hong sam nu ziam? ci kong dong hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 30 Taciang Cornelius in, a bosa ni li lai in hi hun ciang dong an ka tang hi; nitak nai thum in ka innsung ah thu ka ngen hi, taciang, en in, puan pak sil mikhat ka mai ah hong ding a,   
\p
\v 31 Cornelius awng, na thungetna hong hong ki za zo a, mizawngte na hu nate Pathian mai ah ki ciamte hi.   
\p
\v 32 Tua ahikom Peter a kici Simon sia hiak ah sam tu in Joppa ah mi sawl in; ama sia tuihui ah savun vawtpa Simon inn ah tung hi: taciang hongpai ciang in ama in thu hong hil tu hi, ci hong son hi.   
\p
\v 33 Tua ahikom tasia pociang in na kungah mi hongpaisak khi hi; taciang nongpai man in pha hi. Tua ahikom tu in Pathian kung pan na thupiak theampo ngai tu in, ka vekpi in hi mun Pathian mai ah om khawm khu hi, ci hi.   
\s1 Gentile Te in Lungdamna Thu Za  
\p
\v 34 Tuazawkciang in Peter in a kam hong a, Pathian sia mi doidan nei ngawl hi, a ci thuman sia ka umhi:   
\p
\v 35 Ama a zakta te le thutanna a vawt minam peuma sia Pathian in sang hi.   
\p
\v 36 Na theampo i Topa: Jesus Christ tungtawn in a ki pualak kilemna thu sia Pathian in Israel te kungah paisak hi:   
\p
\v 37 Tua ka son thu note in na he uh a, John in tui a phum zawk ciang Galilee pan kipan, Judah ngamsung theampo ah a tangko thu a hi;   
\p
\v 38 Nazareth mi Jesus sia Pathian in Tha Thiangtho le vangletna taw sathau buak hi: napha vawt in pai a, doai i nencip te theampo damsak hi; banghangziam cile Ama sia Pathian in ompui hi, ci thu a hihi.   
\p
\v 39 Kote sia Jerusalem pan kipan in Judah ngamsung ah a vawt theampo i tetti te ka hi uh hi; amate in Jesus that uh a, thing tungah khai uh hi:   
\p
\v 40 Pathian in Ama sia ni thum ni ciang in thokiksak a, a kilang in lak hi;   
\p
\v 41 Mi theampo tungah hi ngawl in, Pathian mai ah tealsa tetti te, thina pan a thawkkik zawkciang in Ama taw a ne le a dawn khawm kote tungah hong lak hi.   
\p
\v 42 Taciang midang te tungah phuang tu le Ama sia mihing le mithi te thukhen tu in Pathian in nasep a piak a hihi, ci tettipang tu in thu hong pia hi.   
\p
\v 43 Ama a umte theampo mihing sim in ama min vangletna taw a mawna uh ki maisak tu hi, ci in kamsang theampo in son uh hi, ci hi.   
\s1 Gentile Te In Tha Thiangtho Sang  
\p
\v 44 Peter in hi thu te a son laitak in Pathian thu a za te tungah Tha Thiangtho hong theng hi.   
\p
\v 45 Taciang Peter taw hongpai te theampo, vunteap tanna a umte in lamdangsa mama uh hi, banghangziam cile Gentile te tungah zong Tha Thiangtho letsong buak hi.   
\p
\v 46 Banghangziam cile amate in, kam tatuam in a pau uh za uh hi. Taciang Pathian pok uh hi. Tua zawkciang in Peter in zo kik a,   
\p
\v 47 Koma bangma in Tha Thiangtho a sang te tuiphumna sang ngawl tu in, khatpo in tui a khak thei tu ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 48 Taciang Peter in Topa min taw tuiphumna sang tu in thupia hi. Tuazawkciang in amate in Peter kungah ni tampi taam tu in ngen uh hi.   
\c 11  
\s1 Peter in Gentile Te Sung A Nasepna te Son  
\p
\v 1 Gentile te in zong Pathian thu sang zo uh hi, ci Judah ngamsung ah a om sawltak te le suapui te in za uh hi.   
\p
\v 2 Taciang Peter sia Jerusalem ah a thet ciang in, vunteap tan te in ama nalh uh a,   
\p
\v 3 Vunteap tan ngawl te kungah na pai a, amate taw an na ne hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 4 Ahihang Peter in tua thu a kipat pan in sonkik a, a ban a ban in amate son siat hi,   
\p
\v 5 Joppa khua ah thu ka nget laitak in, ka mangmuna sungah, puanlam zai mama taw a kibang kingli nei na koina khat van pan hong ki khiasuk a, ka kungah hong theng hi:   
\p
\v 6 A tungah phatak in ka en a, ka ngaisut ciang in, a sungah leitung nganhing peang li nei a tatuam, sapi te, a bokvak te le van a leang vacim te ka mu hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang aw khat ka za a, Peter awng, tho in, ngo in a, ne in, hong ci hi.   
\p
\v 8 Ahihang keima in, hi ngawl hi, Topa awng: banghangziam cile a nin, ahibale, a thiangtho ngawl peuma ka kamsung ah bangmahun in tum ngei ngawl hi, ka ci hi.   
\p
\v 9 Ahihang van pan in tua aw in, Pathian i a thianthosak te nangma in nin hi ci heak in, ci in hong zo kik hi.   
\p
\v 10 Hisia bang in thumvei dong hong ci hi: taciang a vekpi in van ah lato kik siat hi.   
\p
\v 11 Taciang, en vun, tasia pociang in Caesarea pan hong kisawl mihing thum te ka omna mun inn ah hong theng uh hi.   
\p
\v 12 Taciang in bangma ngaisun nawn ngawl in amate taw pai tu in Thaa in hong sawl hi. Tuabek domngawl in hi suapui luk te in hong zui uh hi, taciang Cornelius innsung ah tum tek khu hi:   
\p
\v 13 Taciang Cornelius in a innsung ah vantungmi a mu na thu hong son hi, tua vantungmi ding a a kungah, Joppa khua ah mi sawl in a, Peter a kici Simon sam in;   
\p
\v 14 Ama in thu hong hil tu a, tabang in nangma le na innkuan bup in ngupna na nga tu uh hi, ci in son hi.   
\p
\v 15 Taciang thuhil ka kipan a, a kipat in kote tungah Tha Thiangtho hong thet bangma in amate tung zong ah theng hi.   
\p
\v 16 Tuazawkciang in, \wj John in tui taw tuiphumna hong pia takpi hi; ahihang note Tha Thiangtho taw tuiphumna na sang tu uh hi, \wj* a ci Topa kammal ka phawkkik hi.   
\p
\v 17 Banghangziam cile Pathian in Topa Jesus Christ a umte tungah letsong a piak sia, kote hongpiak taw a kibang a hihi; Pathian khak zo tu in keima sia akua khi ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 18 Amate in hi thu te a zak uh ciang in, thim khipkhep in om uh a, Pathian in Gentile mite zong nuntakna atu maw ki sikkik na pia zohi, ci in Pathian poktek uh hi.   
\s1 Antioch Pawlpi  
\p
\v 19 Stephen thu pan vawtsiatna hang in mun tatuam ah a ki thethang te sia, Phoenicia, Cyprus le Antioch ciang dong pai uh a, Pathian thu midang te tungah hil ngawl in Judah mite tung bek ah hil uh hi.   
\p
\v 20 Ahihang Cyprus le Cyrene a om mi pawlkhat te in, Antioch a thet ciang in, Greek te paupui a, Topa Jesus thuhil hi.   
\p
\v 21 Taciang Topa khut amate tungah om hi: tabang in mi tampi te in um uh a, Topa kungah hong heakkik uh hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tuazawkciang in hi thupha sia Jerusalem pawlpi dong ah hong theng hi: taciang amate in Antioch dong pai tu in Barnabas sawl uh hi.   
\p
\v 23 Antioch ah Barnabas a thet ciang in Pathian i hesuakna mu a, angtang mama hi, taciang amate theampo in thinsung takpi taw Topa beal tu in hanthawn hi.   
\p
\v 24 Banghangziam cile Barnabas sia mipha hi a, Tha Thiangtho le upna taw kidim hi: taciang mi tampi te Topa kungah kibelap hi.   
\p
\v 25 Tuazawkciang in Barnabas sia Saul zong tu in Tarsus ah pai hi:   
\p
\v 26 A mu ciang in Antioch ah paipui hi. Ama te sia kum khat sung buppi pawlpi taw kipawlkhawm uh a, mi tampi te thuhil hi. Taciang nungzui te sia, Christian te, a kici phitbel na sia Antioch khua ah a hihi.   
\p
\v 27 Tua hun sung in kamsang te sia Jerusalem pan in Antioch ah hongpai uh hi.   
\p
\v 28 Amate sung pan Agabus a kici kamsang khat hong ding a, leitung mun theampo ah kialpi tung tu hi, ci in thaa in telsak hi: tua kialpi sia Claudius Caesar hun lai in tung hi.   
\p
\v 29 Nungzui te in amate hi thei za tek taw Judah ngam a om suapui te hu na thak tu in khensatna nei tek uh a:   
\p
\v 30 Amate in upa te kungah Barnabas le Saul te khut tungtawn in thak uh hi.   
\c 12  
\s1 James Thina le Peter Thongtakna Thu  
\p
\v 1 Tua hun pawl in Herod kumpipa in pawlpi sung mi pawlkhat te vawtsiat tu in man hi.   
\p
\v 2 Taciang John i suapuipa James sia namsau taw that hi.   
\p
\v 3 Hi thu in Judah mite lungkimsak hi, ci a mu ciang in, Peter zong mat thua sawm hi. Tol saw ngawl anluum poai hun sung a hihi.   
\p
\v 4 Peter a mat zawkciang in thongtaksak a, ngalkap sawm le luk tei cin tu in ap hi; paisanpoai zawkciang in mihon mai ah pusua tu in ngeal hi.   
\p
\v 5 Tua ahikom Peter sia thong sungah koi nginge hi: ahihang pawlpi te in ama atu in Pathian tungah tatsat ngawl in thungetsak uh hi.   
\s1 Peter Thong Sungpan Suakta  
\p
\v 6 Taciang Herod in a pusua tu ni zan ciang in, Peter sia ngalkap ni te ki laklaw ah thikkol ni taw hen in mu hi: a cingte in kongkha maipan in thonginn cing nginge uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 En vun, Topa vantungmi a kungah hongpai a, thonginn sungah khuavak tang hi: Peter pang pan in beang a, thosak hi, taciang manlang in tho in, ci hi. Taciang in a khut pan thikkhau te tak hi.   
\p
\v 8 Vantungmi in ama kungah, na kawngkhau kil in a, na peangdap bul in, ci hi. Taciang a son bang in Peter in vawt hi. Na puan sil in a, hong zui tan, ci hi.   
\p
\v 9 Peter pusuak in, vantungmi zui hi; taciang vantungmi i vawt teng sia a tatak hi, ci a he bua hi; ahihang mangmu bang in ki ngaisun hi.   
\p
\v 10 Inn doi khat na le doi ni na a kan zawkciang in, khuapi sung paina thik kongpi dong theng hi; tua thik kongpi sia amathu in kihong a: amate a puasang ah pusuak uh hi, taciang lampi khat dungzui in a pai zawk uh ciang; vantungmi in Peter nusia hi.   
\p
\v 11 Peter a khang hong ciim a, a tel thiang kik ciang, tu in a thiangtak in ka tel hi, Topa in Ama vantungmi sawl in, Herod khut le Judah mite lametna pan in hong suatak zo hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 12 Peter in hi thu a ngaisut zawkciang in, Mark a kici John nu Mary te inn ah pai hi; tua mun ah mi tampi te thungen in ki khawmtua uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Taciang Peter in kongpi i kongkha a kik ciang in, Rhoda a kici naseam nu in ngai tu in pai hi.   
\p
\v 14 Taciang Rhoda in Peter aw hi, ci a heak ciang in, lungdam lei ahikom kongpi hong ngawl in, innsung ah tai hi, taciang kongpi mai ah Peter ding hi, ci in son hi.   
\p
\v 15 Amate in, mawmaw ni hi, ci uh hi. Ahihang, a tatak a hihi, ci valeng hi. Tuazawkciang in amate in, ama i vantungmi hi tu hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 16 Ahihang Peter in king top lai hi: taciang amate in kongkha a hon uh ciang in, Peter mu uh a, lamdangsa mama uh hi.   
\p
\v 17 Ahihang Peter in a thim natu in a khut taw lak a, Topa in thong sung pan bangbang in pusua, ci thu amate tungah pualak hi. Taciang James le suapui te kungah pai tavun a hi thu te son tavun, ci hi. Taciang amate pusuak uh a mundang ah pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 18 Khua a vak pociang Peter sia bangsuak ci thu taw kisai in ngalkap te sungah buaina lianpi hong piang hi.   
\p
\v 19 Herod in Peter a zon ciang in, mu ngawl a, a cing te thusit in, thalup natu thu pia hi. Taciang Herod sia Judah ngam pan pusuak a Caesarea ah pai a, tua mun ah tam hi.   
\s1 Herod Thi  
\p
\v 20 Herod sia Tyre le Sidon mite tungah nasiatak in lungkim ngawl hi: ahihang amate thu kisitak in Herod kungah hongpai uh hi, taciang kumpipa lupna inndoi cingpa Blastus pawlvawt uh in, kilemna ngen uh hi; banghangziam cile amate ngam sia Herod ngam sung pan hongpai an le tui taw nungta a hi uh hi.   
\p
\v 21 A ciangtan ni in Herod sia kumpi puan taw ki pua a, kumpi tokhum tungah to in mipi te tungah thu son hi.   
\p
\v 22 Taciang mipite in, hisia sia mihing aw hi ngawl hi, pathian aw hi, ci in au uh hi.   
\p
\v 23 Tasia pociang Topa vantungmi in Herod vel hi, banghangziam cile ama in Pathian minthanna pia ngawl hi: ama sia than in ne a, thi hi.   
\p
\v 24 Ahihang Pathian thu khang in ki zel hi.   
\p
\v 25 Barnabas le Saul sia amate nasep a man uh ciang in Jerusalem pan hong heakkik uh a, Mark a kici John hong tonpui uh hi.   
\c 13  
\s1 Barnabas le Saul  
\p
\v 1 Antioch pawlpi sungah, kamsang le sya pawlkhat om hi; amate sia Barnabas, Niger a kici Simeon, Cyrene khuami Lucius, ngam uk Herod taw a khang khawm pa Manaen le Saul te a hihi.   
\p
\v 2 Amate sia Topa naseam uh a, an a tan uh ciang in, Tha Thiangtho in Barnabas le Saul sia amate ka sap nathu nasep seam tu in a tuam in hong koi tuamsak tavun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 3 Taciang amate antang in thu a nget zawk uh ciang, Barnabas le Saul tungah khut nga in, paisak uh hi.   
\s1 Cyprus Theng  
\p
\v 4 Tha Thiangtho in a sawl bangma in, Barnabas le Saul sia Seleucia ah pai uh a; tua mun pan in Cyprus ah tembaw taw pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Taciang amate Salamis ah a om uh laitak in, Judah te synagogue te sungah Pathian thuhil uh hi: taciang amate a hu tu in John zong om hi.   
\p
\v 6 Tuikul sung theampo pai uh a, Paphos dong theng uh hi, tua mun ah mitbum thiam, leilot kamsang, Judah mi Bar-jesus a kici khat taw ki mu uh hi:   
\p
\v 7 Ama sia Sergius Paulus a kici mipil ngam ukpa taw om khawm hi; tua Sergius Paulus in Pathian thu a zak nop man in Barnabas le Saul sam hi.   
\p
\v 8 Ahihang a min khiakna mitbum thiam a kici Elymas in, ngam ukpa a upna pan ki khealsak tu in Barnabas le Saul te khak hi.   
\p
\v 9 Tuazawkciang in Paul zong a kici Saul sia Tha Thiangtho taw kidim in, Elymas tangtak in en a,   
\p
\v 10 Nang doaimangpa tapa, leilot thu le seksolna taw a kidim, phatngawlna theampo i ngal, Topa lampi pha te suksiatna pan in tawlnga ngawl lai tu ni ziam?   
\p
\v 11 Tu in, en in, Topa khut na tungah om hi, na mittaw tu a, a ciangtan hun sung theampo ni na mu batu hi, ci hi. Taciang thakhatthu in a tungah meikai le khuamial hong theng a; a khut pan a len tu te zong in pai hi.   
\p
\v 12 Ngam ukpa in a vawt te a mu ciang in um a, Topa hilna\f + \fr 13:12 \fq Hilna \ft Dontrine\f* te lamdangsa mama hi.   
\s1 Pisidia Ngam Antioch Theng  
\p
\v 13 Tu in Paul le a lawm te sia Paphos pan in ngunkuang taw pai uh a, Pamphylia ngam Perga theng uh hi: taciang John sia amate kung pan paikhia in Jerusalem ah cia kik hi.   
\p
\v 14 Ahihang Perga pan a pai uh ciang in, Pisidia ngam Antioch theng uh a, sabbath ni in synagogue sungah tum in to hi.   
\p
\v 15 Taciang thukham le kamsang te a sim zawkciang ulian te in ngual paisak a, no u le nau te, mite atu in hanthotna kammal nei na hi uh le, son vun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 16 Taciang Paul dingto in, a khut van hi, Israel mite le no Pathian zakta te, ngai vun.   
\p
\v 17 Hi Israel mite Pathian in i pu le pa te teal a, Egypt ngam ah peamta bang in a om laitak in lamsang hi, taciang a ban sangpi taw Egypt ngam pan in pusua hi.   
\p
\v 18 Taciang senneal ngam sungah kum sawmli kiim anvak hi.   
\p
\v 19 Canaan ngam a om minam sali te a suksiat zawkciang in, amate ngam sia aisan in hawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 20 Tuazawkciang in kamsang Samuel hun hong thet ma kum zali le sawm nga sung, Pathian in thukhenmang te pia hi.   
\p
\v 21 Tuazawkciang in amate in kumpi ngen uh a: Pathian in Benjamin minam Kish i tapa Saul sia kum sawmli sung pia hi.   
\p
\v 22 Saul a hepkhiat zawkciang Pathian in David sia amate kumpi tu in lamsang hi; taciang ama thu Pathian in tettipang a, ka lungtang bang a nei Jesse tapa David ka mu zo hi, ama in ka deina theampo khuangkhim tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 23 Pathian in ama kamciam bang in Israel te ngumtu David suan Jesus tungding hi:   
\p
\v 24 Jesus hongpai ma in John in mawna ki sikkik na taw kisai tuiphumna thu Israel mite theampo tungah hil masa zo hi.   
\p
\v 25 Taciang John in a nasep a man tu ciang in, note in keima kua nong ci uh ziam? Keima sia Ama ka hi bua hi. Ahihang, en vun, ka nung pan in khat hongpai a, a peangdap khau sutsak tu zong ka kilawm bua hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 26 U le nau te awng, Abraham tate le note sungah Pathian a zakta te, hi ngupna thu sia note tungah hong kipuak a hihi.   
\p
\v 27 Banghangziam cile Jerusalem a omte le ulian te in Jesus a heak ngawl uh hang ahizong, sabbath ni sim in a sim kamsang te kammal te zong a heak ngawl lai uh hu in, amate in Jesus mawsak in kamsang te thu tangtungsak uh hi.   
\p
\v 28 Amate in Jesus tungah thi tak mawna a mu bua uh hi, ahihang Ama sia that tu in Pilate kungah ngen uh hi.   
\p
\v 29 Jesus thu a ki atkholsa theampo te sia amate in a tangtunsak zawk uh ciang, thing tung pan in khiasuk uh a, than ah vui uh hi.   
\p
\v 30 Ahihang Pathian in Ama sia thina pan thokiksak hi:   
\p
\v 31 Ama taw Galilee pan Jerusalem dong a pai te in, ni tampi sung mu uh a, tua te sia midang te tungah Ama i tetti te a hi uh hi.   
\p
\v 32 Taciang note tungah lungdamna thupha kote in kong tangko uh hi, tua thu sia i pu le pa te tung a kivawt kamciam a hihi,   
\p
\v 33 Tua thu sia Pathian in ko a tate kungah Jesus a thawkiksak na tungtawn in khuagkhimsak hi; Psalm ni na sungah, Nangma sia ka Tapa na hihi, tu ni in kong nei zo hi, ci in ki atkhol hi.   
\p
\v 34 Taciang Ama sia muat ngawl tu in thina pan a thawkik na thu taw kisai in, David i a muantak hesuakna kong pia tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 35 Mundang Psalm sung ma ah, na mi Thiangtho a muatthong tu na oai bua hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 36 Banghangziam cile David in Pathian deina bang in ama hun mihing te atu na a sep zawkciang mu a, a pu le pa te kungah vui in a pumpi muat hi:   
\p
\v 37 Ahihang Pathian in a thawkiksak pa sia, a pumpi muat ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 38 Tua ahikom u le nau te, hisia pa tungtawn in note tungah maw maisakna thu kong hil uh hi, ci kong hesak hi:   
\p
\v 39 Moses thukham tungtawn in na san thei ngawl uh thutang suana sia Jesus upna tungtawn in a um theampo na theampo pan in thutang suana nga hi.   
\p
\v 40 Tua ahikom kamsang te sonkhol nate note tungah hong thet thei ngawl natu in;   
\p
\v 41 En vun, no ngual selno thei te, lamdangsa vun a, lalcip tavun: banghangziam cile no hun sungah, ka vawt nasep sia bangbang po ahizong na um bua tu uh hi, a ci thu sia kidawm vun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 42 Taciang Judah te synagogue sung pan a pusua ciang in, Gentile mite in mai sabbath ni ciang in hi thu te hil tu in ngen uh hi.   
\p
\v 43 Mipi te kikhop a man uh ciang in, Judah mi tampi le Judah biakna sung a tum Gentile te in Paul le Barnabas te zui uh hi: Paul le Barnabas in Pathian thuthiamna sungah om suak tu in hanthawn uh hi.   
\s1 Paul Sia Gentile te Sang ah Kihei  
\p
\v 44 A mai nipi Sabbath ni ciang in Pathian thu ngai tu in tua khuapi sung om buppi phial hongpai uh hi.   
\p
\v 45 Ahizong Judah mite in mihonpi a mu uh ciang in, hazatna taw kidim uh a, Paul i thuhil nate langpan le sonsia in pau uh hi.   
\p
\v 46 Tuazawkciang in Paul le Barnabas te hangsan seseam uh a, Pathian thu note kong hil phot uh kul hi: ahihang note in na vawk uh a, noma le noma tawntung nuntakna nga tu kiphu ngawl in thu na khen uh hi, en vun, ko Gentile te sangah ka kihei zo uh hi.   
\p
\v 47 Banghangziam cile Topa in thu hongpiakna ah, Gentile mite khuavak hi tu in, lei mong khat dong ngupna atu hi tu in kong koi zo hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 48 Hi thu sia Gentile te in a zak uh ciang in, lungdam mama uh a, Topa thu poktek uh hi: taciang tawntung nuntakna nga tu in a koi sa te in um uh hi.   
\p
\v 49 Topa thu sia tua ngamsung theampo ah kizel hi.   
\p
\v 50 Ahihang Judah mite in biakna sang a ki pumpiak te le a zatakhuai nupi te, khuasung a om ulian te hanthawn uh hi, taciang Paul le Barnabas te nasia seseam in vawtsia uh a, amate ngamsung pan in hawlkhia uh hi.   
\p
\v 51 Ahihang Paul le Barnabas te in a peang tung a bang leivui te thin uh a, Iconium sangah pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 52 Taciang nungzui te sia lungdamna le Tha Thiangtho taw kidim uh hi.   
\c 14  
\s1 Iconium Theng  
\p
\v 1 Iconium ah Paul le Barnabas te a ni in Judah te synagogue sungah paikhawm uh a, thuhil uh hi. Tabang in Judah mite le Greek mite mihon tampi in um uh hi.   
\p
\v 2 Ahihang a um ngawl Judah mite in Gentile mite hanthawn uh a, a um suapui te langpan nopna thinsung phangawl nei tu in vawt uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Tua ahikom amate in Topa sungah hangsantak in thuhil uh a, hun saupi sung tam uh hi, tabang in Pathian hesuakna thu tettipanna atu in musakna te le nalamdang te amate khut tungtawn in vawt thei na pia hi.   
\p
\v 4 Ahihang khuapi sung a om mihonpi te kikhen uh hi: pawlkhat te in Judah mite sang pang uh a, a dang pawlkhat te in sawltak te sang pang uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Gentile mite, Judah mite le lampui te in amate selno uh a, suangtum taw sep tu in a del uh ciang,   
\p
\v 6 Amate in he uh a, Lycaonia ngamsung a om Lystra khua, Derbe khua le a kimlepam ngam te ah tai uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang tua mun ah lungdamna thupha hil uh hi.   
\s1 Peangbaipa Dam  
\p
\v 8 Lystra ah a khealzaw, a nu sung pan a sua pan kipan a peangbai a, a vak ngei ngawl mi khat om hi:   
\p
\v 9 Tuapa in Paul thuhilna za hi: Paul in ama sia tangtak in en a, dam natu upna nei hi, ci a heak ciang in,   
\p
\v 10 Na peang tungah a tangtak in ding in, ci in a ngingtak in sawl hi. Taciang tua pa tawn in lampai hi.   
\p
\v 11 Mihon te in Paul i na vawt a mu uh ciang in, amate Lycaonia kam taw, pathian te mihing bang in eite kungah hong tuaksuk uh hi, ci in a ngingtak in au uh hi.   
\p
\v 12 Amate in Barnabas sia, Jupiter, ci uh hi; Paul sia a thuhilpi ahikom in Mercurius, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Tuazawkciang in a khua mai ah a om Jupiter thiampi in khuital le pakkual te kongpi ah paipui a, mihon te taw biakpiakna piak sawm hi.   
\p
\v 14 Tua thu sawltak te, Paul le Barnabas in a zak uh ciang in, a nik le puan te eau keak uh hi, taciang mihon sungah tai kawm in au uh a,   
\p
\v 15 Banghang in hibang te vawt nu ziam? kote zong note bangma ka hi uh hi, hi a thupi ngawl nate pan in vantung, leitung, tuipi le a sung om theampo a vawt a nungta Pathian sangah kihei tu in note tungah thu ka hil uh hi:   
\p
\v 16 Abosa hun sungah Pathian in minam theampo te amate lampi tek ah paisak hi.   
\p
\v 17 Ahihang Pathian in Ama le Ama sia tetti om ngawl in koithong ngawl a na pha vawt hi, van pan in nguatui le anlak hun te hongpia a, eite i thinsung te an le lungdamna taw hong dimsak hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 18 Taciang hi thu te hil uh a, mipi te in amate tungah biakpiakna vawt ngawl tu in khak zo vamial uh hi.   
\s1 Paul Suangtum Taw Deang  
\p
\v 19 Taciang Antioch le Iconiam ah Judah mi pawlkhat te in, mihon te hanthawn uh a, Paul sia suangtum taw a den zawk uh ciang in, thi zo sa uh a, khua puasang ah kaikeak uh hi.   
\p
\v 20 Ahihang nungzui te a kiimkot ah a din tek uh laitak in thoto a, khuasung ah tum hi: taciang a zingciang in Barnabas taw Derbe ah pai uh hi.   
\s1 Syria Ngam Antioch ah Heakkik  
\p
\v 21 Paul le Barnabas in Derbe khua ah lungdamna thu hil uh a, mi tampi a hil zawk uh ciang in, Lystra, Iconiam le Antioch ah heakkik uh hi.   
\p
\v 22 Nungzui te nuntakna kipsak uh a, upna sungah om paisuak tu le Pathian kumpingam sungah haksatna tampi kantan in i tum hamtang tu hi, ci in hanthawn uh hi.   
\p
\v 23 Taciang amate in pawlpi tatuam ah upa te nasep pia hi, taciang antang in thungetsak a, amate upna Topa tungah ap uh hi.   
\p
\v 24 Taciang amate in Pisidia ngam sung theampo a kantan zawk uh ciang in, Pamphylia theng uh hi.   
\p
\v 25 Perga ah thu a hil zawk uh ciang in, Attalia ah pai uh hi:   
\p
\v 26 Tua mun pan in tembaw taw Antioch sangah pai uh a, Antioch ah amate sepnasa te a seam tu in Pathian i thuthiamna sungah apna a neisakna mun a hihi.   
\p
\v 27 Taciang amate Antioch a thet uh ciang in, pawlpi munkhat ah kaikhawm uh a, Pathian in amate taw a sep uh te Gentile te kungah upna kongkha a honsak na thu te son uh hi.   
\p
\v 28 Tua mun ah a nungzui te taw hun tampi omkhawm uh hi.   
\c 15  
\s1 Jerusalem ah Thu Kikupna  
\p
\v 1 Judah ngam pan hongpai mi pawlkhat te in, Moses thukham bang in vunteap na tan bua uh le, ngupna nga thei ngawl tu nu hi, ci in suapui te hil uh hi.   
\p
\v 2 Amate Paul le Barnabas taw thu kisik ngawl na le ki nial na nasia mama nei uh ahikom in, Antioch a om pawlpi te in Paul, Barnabas le mi pawlkhat te hi thudokna taw kisai Jerusalem ah sawltak te le upa te kungah then tu in khensat uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Pawlpi in lamkal ah amate tha uh a, Phoenicia le Samaria kantan in pai hi, taciang Gentile te i kikhealna thu pualak uh hi: taciang suapui te theampo nasiatak in lungdamsak uh hi.   
\p
\v 4 Amate Jerusalem a thet uh ciang in pawlpi, sawltak te le upa te in muak uh a, Pathian in amate tungtawn a vawt nate theampo son uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Ahihang Pharisee te sungpan thu um pawlkhat te in Gentile thu umte sia vunteap tan kul a, Moses thukham zong zui tu in thupiak kul hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 6 Taciang hi thu ngaisun khawm tu in sawltak te le upa te munkhat ah ki kaikhawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Thu tampi a ki nial zawk uh ciang, Peter ding a, amate tung ah, u le nau te awng, Gentile mite in keima kam pan in lungdamna thupha za uh a, a up theina tu in, tuma hiat in Pathian in eite sung pan keima hong teal hi, ci na he uh hi.   
\p
\v 8 Taciang thinsung a he Pathian in tettipang a, eite tungah hongpiak bang in amate zong Tha Thiangtho pia hi;   
\p
\v 9 Taciang eite le amate kilaklaw ah ki bat ngawlna bangma koi ngawl a, upna tungtawn in amate thinsung te thiangthosak hi.   
\p
\v 10 Tua ahikom, tu in, i pu le pa te le eite in zong i puak zawk ngawl hakkol sia nungzui te ngawng ah koi in banghang Pathian ze-et nu ziam?   
\p
\v 11 Ahihang Topa Jesus Christ i thuthiamna tungtawn in amate ngupna a nga uh bangma in eite zong i nga tu hi, ci in ka um hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 12 Tuazawkciang in Paul le Barnabas te in Gentile te sungah Pathian in amate zang in a vawt nalamdang tatuam te a son uh ciang in, mihon pi te in thim khipkhep in ngai uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Amate thim khipkhep in a om zawk uh ciang in, James in, u le nau te awng, hong ngai tavun:   
\p
\v 14 Ama min atu mi teal tu in Pathian in amasabel in Gentile mite tungah a pai na thu Simon in hong pualak zo hi.   
\p
\v 15 Taciang hi thu sia kamsang te kammal in zong lungkim uh a,   
\p
\v 16 Hi thu zawkciang in kong paikik tu a, a puksa David i biakbuk ka sa kik tu hi; taciang a lal sa sia kasakik tu a, ka dingsak kik tu hi:   
\p
\v 17 Tabang in a tanglai mihing te le Ama min taw a sap Gentile te theampo in Topa zong tu uh hi, ci in hi thu te theampo a vawt Topa in ci hi.   
\p
\v 18 Pathian in leitung piancil pan in a nasep theampo he siat hi, ci ki at zo hi.   
\p
\v 19 Tua ahikom keima i thukhenna sia, Gentile mite sung pan in Pathian sangah a kihei te nawngkaisak bua tawng:   
\p
\v 20 Ahihang milim taw in a thiangtho ngawl te, paktat mawna, tawlsan in a kithat sa te le thisan te pial tu in lai kong thak zaw hi.   
\p
\v 21 Banghangziam cile Moses i thukham sia nidang pek pan in khua tatuam ah ki hil a, synagogue te sung zong ah sabbath nisim in ki sim tawntung hi, ci hi.   
\s1 Gentile Thu Um Mite Laithak  
\p
\v 22 Tuazawkciang in amate sung pan in a tealsa te, suapui te sungah a thupibel Judah a kici Barsabas le Silas te sia, Paul le Barnabas te taw Antioch ah paisak tu in, sawltak te le elder te pan kipan pawlpi buppi in lungkim uh hi:   
\p
\v 23 Taciang amate in hibang in laithak at uh a, sawltak te, elder te le suapui te in Antioch, Syria le Cilicia a om Gentile suapui te hong paupui khu hi:   
\p
\v 24 Kote kung pan in mi pawlkhat te note kungah hongpai uh a, koma thupiak hi ngawl napi, vunteap na tan hamtang uh kul hi, ciang thukham zong na zui hamtang uh kul hi, ci in hong sawl na kammal in note hong nawngkaisak a, na nuntakna uh hong susia hi, ci thu ka za uh hi:   
\p
\v 25 Munkhat ah thu kisi in omkhawm tek a, ka teal uh mihing te, ka it mama uh Barnabas le Paul taw note kungah kong paisak tu uh pha ka sa uh hi.   
\p
\v 26 Amate sia i Topa Jesus Christ min atu in a nuntakna dong a pia ngam te a hi uh hi.   
\p
\v 27 Tua ahikom Judah le Silas te kong paisak uh a, lai kong thak uh bangma in amate in a kam uh taw hongson tu uh hi.   
\p
\v 28 Banghangziam cile note tungah hi a kisam nate simngawl a lianzaw vanngit kong sot ngawl tu uh sia Tha Thiangtho le kote in pha kasa uh hi;   
\p
\v 29 Tabang in note in milim tungah na piak uh sa te, thisan, tawlsan in a kingo sa te le paktat mawna te pial vun: tabang te pan in noma le noma na ki keamcing uh le, a pha ngamta na hi uh hi. Na damtek tavun, ci in laithak at uh hi.   
\p
\v 30 Tua ahikom amate a paikhiat uh ciang in Antioch theng uh hi: mihon te munkhat ah a ki kaikhop zawk uh ciang in, laithak sia pia uh hi:   
\p
\v 31 Tua laithak a sim zawk uh ciang in, henepna thu ahikom in lungdam mama uh hi.   
\p
\v 32 Taciang Judah le Silas te zong kamsang te ahi uh bangma in, suapui te thu tampi taw hanthawn uh a, kipsak uh hi.   
\p
\v 33 Tua mun ah tawlkhat sung a om zawk uh ciang in, suapui te kung pan sawltak te kungah thinnuam takin paisak uh hi.   
\p
\v 34 Ahihang Silas sia tua mun ah om nuam lai hi.   
\p
\v 35 Paul le Barnabas te Antioch ah omsuak a, midang tampi te taw Topa thuhil in tangko uh hi.   
\s1 Paul le Barnabas Kikhen  
\p
\v 36 Tawlkhat sung zawkciang in, Paul in Barnabas kungah, Topa thu i hil na uh mun khua tatuam ah suapui te ve tu in paikik tawng, bangbang in om ziam, ci en tawng, ci hi.   
\p
\v 37 Taciang Barnabas in Mark a kici John sia amate taw tonpui tu in ngaisun hi.   
\p
\v 38 Ahihang Paul in Pamphylia pan in amate taw kikhen a, nasep na mun ah a pai ngawl hu in, amate taw tonpui tu phangawl hi, ci ngaisun hi.   
\p
\v 39 Tua thu Paul le Barnabas nasiatak in ki nial uh a, khat le khat kikhen uh hi: taciang Barnabas in Mark tonpui a, Cyprus sangah tembaw taw pai hi;   
\p
\v 40 Taciang Paul in Silas teal a, suapui te i Pathian thuthiamna sungah apna taw in pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 41 Taciang Syria le Cilicia ngamsung theampo ah pai kakoai uh a, pawlpi te kipsak uh hi.   
\c 16  
\s1 Timothy in Paul le Silas te Zui  
\p
\v 1 Paul sia Derbe le Lystra theng hi: taciang, en vun, nungzui khat om a, a min sia Timothy kici hi, a nu sia Judah mi hi a, thu um mi a hihi; ahihang a pa sia Greek mi a hihi:   
\p
\v 2 Lystra le Iconium a om suapui te in Timothy sia phatson mama uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Timothy sia Paul in tonpui nuam ahikom in a vunteap tansak hi, banghangziam cile tua kiim a om Judah mite theampo in a pa sia Greek mi hi, ci he uh hi.   
\p
\v 4 Amate khuapi tatuam te ah a pai uh kawm in, Jerusalem ah a om sawltak te le upa te in zui tu le kepcing tu in a khensat uh thu sia, a pai na uh khua tatuam te ah ap uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Tua ahikom pawlpi te upna sungah kho uh a, nisim in khang uh hi.   
\s1 Macedonia Pan Sapna  
\p
\v 6 Tu in amate Phrygia le Galatia ngam a kantan zawk uh ciang in, Tha Thiangtho in Asia ngam ah Pathian thuhil tu khak hi,   
\p
\v 7 Mysia ngam a thet zawk uh ciang in, Bithynia ngamsung ah paisawm uh hi: ahihang Thaa in a pai tu uh oai ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 8 Taciang amate Mysia ngam kantan uh a, Troas theng uh hi.   
\p
\v 9 Tua zan in Paul in mangmu hi; Macedonia mi khat ding a, Macedonia ah hongpai tan a, kote hong hu tan, ci in ngen hi.   
\p
\v 10 Paul in a mangmu zawkpo ciang in, Macedonia ah lungdamna thupha tangko tu in Topa in hong sam hi, ci thiangtak in tel ka hi uhkom, pai tu in ka hanciam uh hi.   
\s1 Lydia in Jesus Um  
\p
\v 11 Tua ahikom Troas pan in ngunkuang taw ka pai uh a, Samotracia ah a tangtan in ka pai uh hi, taciang a zingciang in Neapolis ka theng uh hi;   
\p
\v 12 Tua mun pan in Macedonia ngamkhen sung pan khuapi lianbel Philippi ka theng uh hi, Philippi khua sia Rome te in ngamkeak in a ukna ngam a hihi: tua khuapi sungah tawlkhat sung ka om uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Sabbath ni in ngunhui khuapi ah ka pai uh hi, thungetna mun ah ka to uh a, hongpai numei te ka paupui uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Taciang Lydia a kici Thyatira khua mi, puan sandup a zuak numei khat om a, ama sia Pathian bia khat a hihi: ama in Paul i thuhilna te ngai tu in Topa in a thinsung honsak hi.   
\p
\v 15 Ama le a innkuanpui te tui a ki phum zawk uh ciang in, Topa tungah muantak hi, ci in nong mu uh ahile, ka inn ah hongpai tavun a, tua mun ah hong taam tavun, ci in hong sam a, hong thum hi.   
\s1 Paul le Silas Philippi Thongsung Ah  
\p
\v 16 Thungen tu ka pai uh ciang in, a sungah maisang thu sonkhol theina thaa nei a, a to te atu in dangka tampi a ngasak naseam numei no khat in hong muak hi:   
\p
\v 17 Ama in Paul le kote nung pan in hongzui a, hi mite sia ngupna lampi hong lak tu a sangbel Pathian i sal te a hi uh hi, ci in au hi.   
\p
\v 18 Taciang ama in hibang in ni tampi sung vawt hi. Ahihang Paul a thin-uk in le-et a, tua thaa kungah, Jesus Christ min taw hi numei sung pan pusuak tu in thu kong pia hi, ci hi. Tuahun laitak lian in pusuak hi.   
\p
\v 19 A to te in dangka tampi nga natu lametna om nawn ngawl hi, ci a mu uh ciang in Paul le Silas te man uh a, thukhen zum ulian te kungah kai uh hi.   
\p
\v 20 Taciang ulian te kungah paipui a, hi Judah mite in i khuapi nasiatak in buaisak hi,   
\p
\v 21 Ko Rome mite in ka san thei ngawl uh le ka zui ngawl uh ngeina te hil hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 22 Taciang mihonpi te hong ding tek uh hi: taciang ulian te in zong a puan uh eaukeaksak uh a, Paul le Silas te vel tu in thupia uh hi.   
\p
\v 23 Amate in nasiatak in a sat zawk uh ciang in, thonginn sungah khia uh a, thong cing pa in phatak a cin natu in vaitha hi:   
\p
\v 24 Thu a vaithak thonginn cingpa in, thonginn doi sungah khumsuk a, a peang te uh peangkol bul in koi hi.   
\s1 Thong Cingpa in Jesus Um  
\p
\v 25 Zan laitak in Paul le Silas te thungen uh a, Pathian pok na lasa khawm uh hi: taciang thongtak te in ngai uh hi.   
\p
\v 26 Thakhatthu in zin nasiatak hong ling a, thong innbul te ki lok hi: tasia pociang in kongkha te a vekpi in ki hong siat a, a ki hen na uh theampo zong ki sut siat hi.   
\p
\v 27 Thongcingpa hong khanglo a, kongkha te a ki hong a mu ciang in, thongtak te taisiat zo sa a, a namsau dok in, ama le ama ki tha sawm hi.   
\p
\v 28 Ahihang Paul ngingtak in au a, nangma le nangma ki vawtsia heak in: banghangziam cile ka vekpi in hi mun ah ka om nginge uh hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 29 Tuazawkciang in thongcingpa in mei ngen a, hong bingbung hi, taciang ling vadil kawm in hongpai a, Paul le Silas te mai ah bok hi,   
\p
\v 30 Taciang amate pusua a, ka topa te awng, ngupna ka nga natu in bang ka vawt tu ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 31 Amate in, Topa Jesus Christ um in a, nangma le na innkuanpui te in ngupna na nga tu uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 32 Taciang Paul le Silas te in ama innsung ah a omte theampo tungah Topa thuhil uh hi.   
\p
\v 33 Tua zan in thongcingpa in amate pusua a, a liamma uh te silsak hi; taciang ama le a innkuanpui theampo tui ki phum pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 34 Saul le Silas sia ama inn ah ciapui a, amate mai ah anlui hi, taciang ama le a innkuanpui theampo in Pathian um uh a, lungdam mama uh hi.   
\p
\v 35 A zingciang in, ulian te in palik mang te sawl a, tua mihing te pusua vun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 36 Taciang thongcingpa in Paul kungah, ulian te in note sam tu in mi sawl hi; tua ahikom tu in pusuak vun a, thinnuamtak in pai vun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 37 Ahihang Paul in amate tung ah, kote sia Rome ngammi hi napi, mawsiatna om ngawlpi kilangtak in hong sat a, thong hong taksak hi; tu in kuama heak ngawl in hong hawlkhia nuam ziam? hi thei ngawl hi; ahihang amate hongpai ta hen a hong suatak tahen, ci hi.   
\p
\v 38 Taciang palik mang te in hi thu a ulian te kungah son uh hi: taciang amate Rome ngam mi hi, ci a zak uh ciang in, ulian te patau mama uh hi.   
\p
\v 39 Taciang amate hongpai uh a, Paul te thum uh hi, taciang suatak uh a, tua khuapi sung pan pusuak tu in sawl uh hi.   
\p
\v 40 Amate thong sung pan pusuak uh ah, Lydia te innsung ah tum uh hi: taciang suapui te a mu uh ciang in heneam uh a, paikik uh hi.   
\c 17  
\s1 Thessalonica Theng  
\p
\v 1 Paul le Silas te Amphipolis le Apollonia a kantan zawk uh ciang in, Thessalonica theng uh hi, tua mun ah Judah te synagogue om hi:   
\p
\v 2 Taciang Paul sia ama ngeina bang in, synagogue sungah tum a, sabbath ni nithum sung amate taw laithiangtho sung thu te kikum uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Christ sia a thuak kul hamtang a hina le thina pan thokik hamtang tu hi; ci in note tungah ka pualak hi Jesus sia Christ a hihi, ci in pualak in hil thiang hi.   
\p
\v 4 Amate sung pan pawlkhat te in um uh a, Paul le Silas te kipawlpui uh hi; taciang tua te sungah biakna sang a kipumpiak Greek mihon tampi le numei lampui tampi kihel uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Ahihang a um ngawl Judah mite in haza uh a, van zuakna lamdung a vakvai mannung ngawl mite sam uh hi, taciang honpi khat hong pha uh a khuapi sungah buaina piangsak uh hi, taciang Jason i inn sim uh a, mipi mai ah pusua tu in zong uh hi.   
\p
\v 6 Taciang amate in a mu ngawl uh ciang in, Jason le suapui pawlkhat te khuapi ulian te kungah kai uh a, hileitung lumlet te himun zong ah hongpai uh hi;   
\p
\v 7 Amate sia Jason in ama inn ah tungsak hi: hi te theampo in Caesar thupiakna te langpan uh a, Jesus a kici a dang kumpi khat om hi, ci uh hi, ci in au lialua uh hi.   
\p
\v 8 Hi thu te mipi te le khuapi ulian te in a zak uh ciang in, buai mama uh hi.   
\p
\v 9 Taciang Jason le a dang te sia a kisam za dangka liausak uh a, tua zawkciang in thaa kik uh hi.   
\s1 Berea Theng  
\p
\v 10 Zan ciang in suapui te in Paul le Silas te Berea ah a zan a zan in paisak uh hi: tua mun a thet uh ciang in Judah mite i synagogue sungah tum uh hi.   
\p
\v 11 Hi te sia Thessalonica mite sang in a thinsung uh phazaw hi, thalawptak in thu ngai uh a, tua a ngai uh thu te a man le man ngawl nisim laithiangtho sungah zong uh hi.   
\p
\v 12 Tua ahikom amate sung panmi tampi in um uh a; a zatak huai Greek nupi pasal tampi zong kihel uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Ahihang Thesslonica a om Judah mite in Berea khua ah zong Paul in Pathian thuhil hi, ci a heak uh ciang in, hongpai uh a, mipi te thawn uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Tua zawk pociang in suapui te in Paul sia tuipi sangah paisak uh hi: ahihang Silas le Timothy sia Berea ah taamlai hi.   
\p
\v 15 Paul a tha te in Athens dong tha uh hi: taciang Silas le Timothy sia manlangtak a pai natu in Paul kung pan thupiak nga uh a, pai uh hi.   
\s1 Athen Theng  
\p
\v 16 Paul in Athen pan Silas le Timothy te ngak in a om laitak, tua khuapi sungah milim biakna bebek om hi, ci a mu ciang in, a thinsung sutha mama hi.   
\p
\v 17 Tua ahikom Judah biakna lampui te taw synagogue sungah thu ki nial uh a, vanzuakna ah a kisikpui te taw nisim in ki nial uh hi.   
\p
\v 18 Tuazawkciang in thu ngaisun thiam Epicurean te le Stoic te taw ki mu uh hi. Taciang pawlkhat te in, hi a papau sia bang son ziam? a dang pawlkhat te zong in, hisia pa sia ngamdang te pathian te thu son hi tu hi, ci uh hi: banghangziam cile Paul in amate tungah Jesus le a thawkikna thu son hi.   
\p
\v 19 Taciang amate in Paul man uh hi, taciang Areopagas ah paipui uh a, hi hilna thak na son te kote zong ka heak tu uh kisam ziam?   
\p
\v 20 Banghangziam cile a tumdang te ka bil uh ah nong zasak hi: hi thu te i deina sia bangziam, ci ka he nuam uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 21 Banghangziam cile Athen mite le leangna te theampo in thuthak son tu, a hibale ngai tu simngawl bangma dang atu amate hun a zang bua uh hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tuazawkciang in Paul sia Mars mual laizang ah ding a, no Athen mite, note sia na theampo nasiatak thuciing cimteam mama te na hi uh hi, ci kong he hi.   
\p
\v 23 Banghangziam cile ka vakawm in biakna sang na hanciam nate uh ka en a, \sc a ki he ngawl pathian atu\sc* ci a ki at biaktau khat ka mu hi. Tua ahikom note in he ngawlpi in na biak uh Pathian thu kong pualak hi.   
\p
\v 24 Tua Pathian sia leitung le a sung om theampo a vawtpa a hihi, ama sia van le lei i Topa hi a, khut taw a kisa biakinn sungah om ngawl hi;   
\p
\v 25 Pathian sia mi theampo tungah nuntakna, husanna le na theampo a piapa ahikom, mihing te khut taw i vawtsak tu bangma kisam ngawl hi;   
\p
\v 26 Taciang Ama in leitung theampo ah a om minam theampo sia thisan khat in vawt a, amate om tu hun te le a om natu mun te zong ngealkholsak siat hi;   
\p
\v 27 Tabang in amate in Topa zong uh a, tham in a mu thei natu a hihi, Pathian sia eite khatsim kuama taw ki khuala ngawl hi:   
\p
\v 28 Banghangziam cile i nungta a, i tuk i dian le i hina theampo sia Ama sungah a hihi; tasia bangma in na laphuak te in zong, eite zong Ama suan te i hihi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 29 Tabang in Pathian suan te i hi man in, mihing te khutthiam le ngaisutna taw a kivawt kham, ngun le suangtum milim bang in Pathian sia i ngaisut tu hi ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 30 Mihing te in Pathian a heak ma hunlai in Pathian in a mu ngawl bang in omthong ngei napi; tu in mun theampo ah a om mi theampo maw ki sikkik natu in thupia hi:   
\p
\v 31 Banghangziam cile nasep a piaksa mihing khat zang in leitung ah thutang suana tungtawn thu a khen tu ni ciangtan zo hi; tua thu sia a ma a hihi, ci in mi theampo tungah kilangsak tu in tua pa sia thina pan thokiksak zo hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 32 Amate in mithi te thawkikna thu a zak uh ciang in, mi pawlkhat te in selno uh hi: a dang te in, hi thu nangtung pan ka za kik nuam uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 33 Taciang Paul sia amate sung pan in pusuak hi.   
\p
\v 34 Ahihang mi pawlkhat te in ama beal uh a, um uh hi: tua te sungah Areopagas mi Dionysius, Damaris a kici nupi khat le midang te zong kihel uh hi.   
\c 18  
\s1 Prisilla le Aquila  
\p
\v 1 Hiteng zawkciang in Paul sia Athens pan pai a, Corinth theng hi;   
\p
\v 2 Taciang Aquila a kici Judah mi khat taw ki mu hi, ama sia Pontus ah a suak hi a, a zi Prisilla taw Italy pan a thet zawk uh ngei ngawl lai hi; banghangziam cile Claudius in Judah mi theampo Rome pan pusuak tu in thupia hi: taciang Paul sia amate kungah hongpai hi.   
\p
\v 3 Amate taw khutthiam kibang ahi uhkom in amate kungah taam a, naseam khawm uh hi: banghangziam cile amate sia puanbuk khui te a hi uh hi.   
\p
\v 4 Sabbath ni sim in synagogue sungah Judah mite le Greek mite thu sonpui in kaizawn tawntung uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Macedonia pan Silas le Timothy te a thet ciang in, Jesus sia Christ hi, ci thu Paul in Judah mite tungah hanciam in tettipang hi.   
\p
\v 6 Amate in Paul langpan uh a, a sonsiat uh ciang in, Paul in a puan thin a, na thisan uh noma lutung ah om tahen; kei ka hile na thisan uh pan ka thiang hi: tu pan kipan in Gentile te kungah ka pai tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang Paul sia tua mun pan pai a, Justus innsung ah tum hi, ama in Pathian bia a, a inn sia synagogue taw kinai na a hihi.   
\p
\v 8 Synagogue makai lianbel Crispus le a innkuanpui theampo in Topa um uh hi; taciang Corinth mi tampi te in zong za in um uh a, tui kiphum uh hi.   
\p
\v 9 Tuazawkciang in Topa in mangmuna taw zan ciang inb Paul paupui a, \wj Lauheak in a, thuhil in, om thong heak in:\wj*   
\p
\v 10 \wj Banghangziam cile keima in kong ompui hi, kuama in hong vawtsia ngawl tu hi: banghangziam cile hi khuapui sungah keima in mi tampi ka nei hi, \wj* ci hi.   
\p
\v 11 Taciang Paul sia tua mun ah kumkhat le tha luk sung om suak a, amate sungah Pathian thuhil hi.   
\p
\v 12 Gallio sia Rome ngam uk a sep lai in, Judah mite in thu kisitak in Paul langpan uh a, thukhenna tokhum mai ah paipui uh a,   
\p
\v 13 Hisia pa in thukham paltan in Pathian bia tu in ngual kaizawn hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Paul pau tu a kipat ciang in, Gallio in Judah mite kungah, hi thu sia a man ngawl le thusia hile, Maw, no Judah mite, note tungah thinsausak tu kisam ci in ngaisun khi hi:   
\p
\v 15 Ahihang hi thu sia na thukham uh sung a thu le min te ki nialna ahile, noma in khensat tawm vun; banghangziam cile kei sia tabang thu te tungah thukhen ngawl tu khi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 16 Taciang amate thukhen zum pan in hawlkhia siat hi.   
\p
\v 17 Tuazawkciang in Greek mite in synagogue makai lianbel Sosthenes man uh a, thukhen na mai ah sat uh hi. Taciang Gallio in hi thu te awlmawk ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 18 Taciang in Paul sia Corinth khua ah tawlkhat sung a om zawkciang in, suapui te nusia a, Pricilla le Aquila te taw Syria ah tembaw taw pai hi; taciang Cenchrea ah a sam met hi: banghangziam cile kamciam na a nei hang a hihi.   
\p
\v 19 Ephesus khua theng uh a, tua mun ah Pricilla le Aquila te nusia hi: ahihang ama vateak synagogue sungah tum in, Judah mite taw thu kikum khawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 20 Amate in ngei zaw hiat om tu a nget uh ciang, thukim pui ngawl hi;   
\p
\v 21 Ahihang kikhenna kam te nusiat a, Jerusalem ah hi poai sia bangbangpo ahizong ka kihel kul hamtang hi; ahihang Pathian deina a om ahile, note kungah heakkik tu khi hi, ci hi. Taciang Ephesus pan in tembaw taw pai hi.   
\p
\v 22 Caesarea a thet ciang in, pawlpi te paupui a, Antioch sangah pai hi.   
\p
\v 23 Tua mun ah tawlkhat sung hun a zak zawkciang in pusuak kik a, nungzui te theampo hanthawn tu in Galatia le Phrygia ngamsung theampo ah pai hi.   
\s1 Apollos  
\p
\v 24 Taciang Alexandria khua ah a suak Judah mi Apollos a kici khat Ephesus ah hong theng hi, ama sia kamthiam mama a, laithiangtho taw kisai zong thahat mama hi.   
\p
\v 25 Hisia pa sia Topa lampi taw kisai phatak a kihil mi a hihi; taciang thaalam ah thalawp mama a, Topa thu te thupitak in a son le a hil pa a hihi, ahihang John i tuiphumna thu bek he hi.   
\p
\v 26 Taciang synagogue sungah hangsantak in thuhil kipan a: Aquila le Pricilla te in a zak uh ciang in, amate kungah sam hi, taciang Pathian lampi a kimtak in hilcian hi.   
\p
\v 27 Apollos sia Achaia ngamkhen ah pai nuam ahikom, Ephesus khua a om suapui te in Achaia a om nungzui te kungah lai thak uh a, Apollos a san natu uh in hanthawn uh hi, a thet ciang in thu um mite sia hesuakna tungtawn in nasiatak in hu hi:   
\p
\v 28 Banghangziam cile Jesus sia Christ hi, ci thu laithiangtho zang in a kilangtak in lak a, Judah mite nasiatak in zo hi.   
\c 19  
\s1 Ephesus Theng  
\p
\v 1 Apollos sia Corinth khua ah a om laitak in, Paul in saksang ngam te kantan a, Ephesus hong theng hi: tua mun ah nungzui pawlkhat te taw kimu uh a,   
\p
\v 2 Amate kungah, na up zawk uh Tha Thiangtho na sang zo uh ziam? ci hi. Taciang amate in Paul tung ah, Tha Thiangtho a om hunlam zong ka za ngei bua uh hi, ci uh ih.   
\p
\v 3 Taciang Paul in amate tung ah, bang tuiphumna sang nu ziam? ci hi. Taciang amate in, John i tuiphumna ka sang uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 4 Tuazawkciang in Paul in hibang in ci hi. John in mawna ki sikkikna tuiphumna hongpia takpi a, mite tungah a nung pan hongpai tu Christ Jesus sia amate in a up tu uh a hihi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 5 Amate in hi thu a zak uh ciang in, Topa Jesus min taw tui ki phum uh hi.   
\p
\v 6 Taciang Paul in amate tungah a khut a ngak ciang in, Tha Thiangtho sia amate tungah hong theng hi; taciang kam tatuam taw in pau uh a, mailam thu zong pualak uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Amate a vekpi in pasal sawmleni khawng a hi uh hi.   
\p
\v 8 Paul sia synagogue sungah tum a, Pathian kumpingam thu taw kisai in thuhil le hanthawn in, tha thum sung hangsantak in thuhil hi.   
\p
\v 9 Ahihang pawlkhat te a thinsung khauh uh a um ngawl in, mipi mai ah tua lampi\f + \fr 19:9 \fq Lampi \ft Thu umte a cinopna hi\f* phat ngawlna thu son uh hi, taciang Paul sia amate kung pan pusuak a, nungzui te tuamkhen in Tyrannus sanginn khat sungah nisim in thu kikum khawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 10 Hi bangin kum ni sung zomsuak uh hi; tua ahikom Asia ngamsung a om Judah mite le Greek mite theampo in Topa Jesus thu za kim uh hi.   
\s1 Sceva Tapa Salite  
\p
\v 11 Pathian in Paul i khut te zang in a tuan in nalamdang te vawt hi:   
\p
\v 12 Ama pumpi pan in dialno le kawngkhau te cina te kungah paipui uh a, cina te sung pan in natna te le doai te pusuak hi.   
\p
\v 13 Mun theampo ah vak a thaa ngilo a hawlkhia Judah mi pawlkhat om hi, thaa ngilo a neite tungah Topa Jesus min lo uh a, Paul i a hil Jesus tungtawn in thu hong pia khu hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Judah mi thiampi lian Sceva tapa sali te in tabang in vawt uh hi.   
\p
\v 15 Taciang tua thaa ngilo in, Jesus ka he hi, taciang Paul zong ka he hi; ahihang note a kuate nu ziam? ci in zo hi.   
\p
\v 16 Taciang a sungah thaa ngilo a neipa sia amate tungpan baw in buan ngawp a, zothal hi, tua ahikom amate tua innsung pan pumnguak le liamma taw tai mang uh hi.   
\p
\v 17 Taciang hi thu sia Ephesus a om Judah mite le Greek mite theampo in he uh hi; taciang amate tungah launa hong theng a, Topa Jesus min pok tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 18 Thu um tampi te hongpai uh a, amate mawna te pualak in a sep a vawt uh te zong pholak uh hi.   
\p
\v 19 Mitbum thiam tampi te zong a laibu te uh munkhat ah hong paipui uh a, mi theampo mai ah mei taw hal uh hi: tua laibu te i man a tuat uh ciang in, ngun dangka then nga man hi.   
\p
\v 20 Tua ahikom Pathian thu in zo a nasiatak in khang uh hi.   
\p
\v 21 Hi thu te a tawp zawk, paul in Macedonia ngam le Achaia ngam te a kantan zawkciang in, Jerusalem ah pai tu in ngealkhol hi, tua mun ah ka thet zawkciang in Rome zong mu hamtang lai tu khi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tua ahikom ama a hu tu te sung pan in, Timothy le Erastus te sia Macedonia ah heakkik uh a; ama sia Asia ngamsung ah tawmvei sung om lai hi.   
\s1 Ephesus ah Buaina  
\p
\v 23 Tua hun in hi lampi\f + \fr 19:23 \fq lampi \ft thu umte a ci nopna hi\f* thu hang in buaina lianpi piang hi.   
\p
\v 24 Banghangziam cile ngun seak thiam Demetrius a kici pa in Artimis doai numei atu in biakinn lim te ngun taw in vawt a, khutthiam neite kungah a met tam mama then hi;   
\p
\v 25 Tua a nasep kibang naseam te kaikhawm a, hi khutthiam tungtawn in hau na i nga hi, ci na he uh hi.   
\p
\v 26 Tua bekdom ngawl, Ephesus bek ah hi ngawl in, Asia ngamsung bup dektak ah, hi Paul in khut taw a ki vawt te Pathian hi ngawl hi, ci a, mi tampi te hanthawn in kikhealsak hi, ci zong mu in na za uh hi:   
\p
\v 27 Tua ahikom i khutthiam sia mannung ngawl a sua tu lauhuai bek domngawl in; Asia ngam theampo le leitung bup i biak Artemis doai nu i biakinn zong ki thusimngawl tu hi, taciang a minthanna susia tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 28 Taciang hi thu te amate in a zak uh ciang in thin-uk na taw kidim uh a, Ephesus mite i Artemis sia thupi hi, ci in au uh hi.   
\p
\v 29 Taciang tua Khuapi sia buaina taw kidim hi: Paul i khualhaw pui Macedonia mi Gaius le Aristarchus te man uh a, poai etna sungah thukimtak in manlangtak in tum tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 30 Paul sia mihon te kungah a tum sawm ciang in, nungzui te in oai ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 31 Taciang Asia ngam ukpa i lawm te zong poai etna sungah tum ngawl tu in a kungah ngual sawl in, ngen hi.   
\p
\v 32 Tua ahikom pawlkhat te in thu khat au uh a, a dang pawlkhat te in thudang au uh hi: banghangziam cile a tamzaw in banghang in ki kaikhawm, ci he ngawl in, mihonpi te buai mama hi.   
\p
\v 33 Judah mite in Alexander sia mipi sung pan in kaikeak a, mai ah sawn uh hi. Taciang Alexander in a khut taw lak a, mipi te kungah ama le ama ki ngum in thuson nuam hi.   
\p
\v 34 Ahihang amate in Alexander sia Judah mi hi, ci a heak uh ciang in, Ephesus mite i Artemis sia thupi hi, ci in a vekpi in nai ni sung aw khat sua in au va nuau uh hi.   
\p
\v 35 Taciang khuapi lai-at pa in mipi te a thim zawkciang in, no Ephesus mite, Ephesus khuapi sia a lian mama Artemis doai nu Jupiter pan in hong tak milim bia hi, ci a he ngawl a kua om ziam?   
\p
\v 36 Hi thu te sia kuama i nial thei ngawl thu ahikom in, na om khipkhep tu uh hi a, bangma ngaisun ngawl in na pheang tat tu uh hi ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 37 Banghangziam cile hi mun ah na paipui uh hi te sia, pawlpi van a suttol te hi ngawl a, na doai nu uh mindaisak te zong hi ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 38 Tua ahikom Demetrius le khutthiam nei te khatpo taw ki langpan in thu a om ahile, thukham sia a ki hong sa in om hi, taciang ngam uk te zong om ahikom in: amate khat le khat thu ki sua khawm ta uh hen.   
\p
\v 39 Ahihang thu dang te taw kisai in na kan nuam uh le, ngeina bang in a ki kaikhawm mipi te in khensat tahen.   
\p
\v 40 Banghangziam cile tu ni i buaina hang in thu dong tu in hong sap tu lauhuai hi, hibang ngeina om ngawl in i kikhoptua na sia a hang son tu le i nei tuan bua hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 41 Hibang in a son zawkciang, a ki kaikhawm te ciakik siat uh hi.   
\c 20  
\s1 Macedonia le Greece Ngam Theng  
\p
\v 1 Buaina a bo zawkciang, Paul in nungzui te a kungah sam a, a koai zawkciang in, Macedonia ah pai tu in pusuak hi.   
\p
\v 2 Tua ngamsung mun tatuam te ah pai a, thu tam mama taw hanthawn in tha a piak zawkciang, Greece ngam theng hi,   
\p
\v 3 Tua mun ah tha thum sung om hi. Syria ah tembaw taw a paisawm ciang in, Judah mite in pang ahikom in Macedonia pan heakkik tu in ngeal hi.   
\p
\v 4 Asia ngamsung a pai ciang in Berea khua mi Sopater; Thessalonica khua mi Aristarchus le Secundus; Derbe khua mi Gaius le Timothy, Asia ngam pan Tychicus le Trophimus te in tonpui hi.   
\p
\v 5 Amate ka mai ah pai masa uh a, Troas pan hong ngak uh hi.   
\s1 Eutychus Inntung Pan Tak  
\p
\v 6 Tol saw ngawl anluum poai ni zawkciang in, Philippi pan in tembaw taw ka pai uh a, ni nga sung ka pai zawk uh ciang amate kung Troas ka theng uh hi, tua mun ah ni sali sung ka om uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Nipi kalkhat sung ni masabel ni in, nungzui te anluum bal tu in a ki kaikhop uh ciang, Paul in amate tungah Pathian thuhil a, a zingciang pai tu hi zo ka hi uhkom in; zankim dong thuhil suak hi.   
\p
\v 8 Amate kikhopna mun inn tung doi ah mei-inn tam mama om hi.   
\p
\v 9 Taciang Eutychus a kici tangval khat a to kawm in, a mutsuak mama hi: taciang Paul in ngei mama thuhil ahikom, lusu in inn dawl thum na pan taksuk a, a thisa in tawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 10 Taciang Paul tuaksuk in, tangval pa tungah bok hi, taciang koai a, Paul in buai heak vun, banghangziam cile a sungah a nuntakna om hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 11 Taciang Paul inn tung a kato kik ciang in, anluum balnen uh a, ne khawm uh hi, khuavak dong ngei mama thu a sonkhop zawkciang in Paul pai hi.   
\p
\v 12 Amate in tangval pa a nungta in hong paipui uh hu in, amate a thin uh nuam mama hi.   
\p
\v 13 Paul muak kawm tu in tembaw taw Assos ah ka pai uh hi: banghangziam cile ama in peang taw pai tu ngaisun ahikom, hong sonkholsa a hihi.   
\p
\v 14 Assos ah Paul taw ka ki situa uh a, ama ka muak uh hi, taciang Mitylene ka theng uh hi.   
\p
\v 15 Tua mun pan in tembaw taw ka pai khawm leleau uh a, a zingciang in Chios ngalkhat ka theng uh hi; taciang a zingciang in Samos ka theng uh a, Trogyllium ah ka ngiak uh hi; taciang a zingciang in Miletus ka theng uh hi.   
\p
\v 16 Banghangziam cile Paul in Asia ah hun zang ngawl tu le Ephesus pan tembaw taw pai tu in ngeal hi: banghangziam cile a suak thei tu ahile, Pentecost ni in Jerusalem ah manlang in theng nuam hi.   
\s1 Paul le Ephsus Upate  
\p
\v 17 Taciang Miletus pan in Ephesus ah mi paisak in, pawlpi upa te samsak hi.   
\p
\v 18 Amate a thet ciang in, Paul in amate tung ah, Asia ngamsung ka thet masabel pan in, note kung ka om sung theampo bangbang in ka om, ci sia na heak uh a hihi,   
\p
\v 19 Thinsung kiniamkhiak le thitui tampi taw Topa na ka seam hi, taciang Judah mite in hong pang tawntung uh ahikom ka tungah mawsiatna te hong theng hi:   
\p
\v 20 Taciang note tungah phattuamna khat zong khet nei ngawl khi hi, ahihang mihonpi te mai ah ahizong, inn khat zawk inn khat ah ahizong, hong lak in hong hil khi hi,   
\p
\v 21 Judah mite le Greek mite tungah zong, Pathian tungah mawmaina le i Topa Jesus Christ tungah upna thu tetti ka pang hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tu in, Jerusalem ah pai tu in Thaa in hong hen a, ka tungah bang thu piang tu, ci zong ka he bua hi:   
\p
\v 23 Ahizong khuapi tatuam ah hencip le haksatna te in hong ngak hi, ci Tha Thiangtho in tettipang hi.   
\p
\v 24 Ahihang Topa Jesus kung pan ka san Pathian thuthiamna lungdamna thupha tetti pan nasep sia, lungdamna taw ka zaw thei natu in, hi thu te in hong lingsak zo ngawl a, ka nuntakna zong pamai ka sa bua hi.   
\p
\v 25 Taciang tu in, en vun, Pathian kumpingam thuhil in ka pai na mun theampo ah note in ka maitang nong mu kik nawn ba tu uh hi, ci ka he hi.   
\p
\v 26 Tua ahikom mi theampo i thisan pan in ka suakta hi, ci in tu ni note tungah tetti kong pang hi.   
\p
\v 27 Banghangziam cile Pathian i tupna a vekpi in note tungah ka pualak tu khet ka nei bua hi.   
\p
\v 28 Tua ahikom Ama thisan taw a lei sa, Pathian pawlpi an vak tu le keamcing tu in Tha Thiangtho in a koi sa note atu in ahizong, tuu hon theampo atu in ahizong, kidawm tavun.   
\p
\v 29 Banghangziam cile ka pai zawkciang in ngia ngilo te note sungah hong tum tu a, tuu hon te khoaikhe ngawl tu hi.   
\p
\v 30 Noma sung mama pan in pawlkhat te pusuak tu uh a, nungzui te kaizawn tu in a man ngawl thu te son tu uh hi.   
\p
\v 31 Tua ahikom en vun, kum thum sung tawntung sun le zan tawlnga ngawl in thitui taw mi theampo kidop natu thu ka hil hi, ci phawk tawntung tavun.   
\p
\v 32 Tu in, suapui te awng, Pathian le Ama thuthiamna kammal kong ap hi, Ama in hong khangtosak zo tu a, mithiangtho te theampo sungah ngamh hong pia tu hi.   
\p
\v 33 Kuama i puansil nikten, le kham le ngun te ka eang bua hi.   
\p
\v 34 Hi ka khut taw keima le ka ompuite kisapna atu in na ka seam hi, ci sia note in na he uh hi.   
\p
\v 35 Tabang in note in zong keima bang naseam a, thaneam te na hu uh kul hi, ci le, \wj Nga na sang in piak na ah thupha tamzaw hi, \wj* ci Topa Jesus i son kammal te na phaw tawntung natu uh in hi thu te theampo a vekpi in kong laksiat zo hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 36 Paul in a thuson man ciang in khupdin a, amate theampo taw thungen khawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 37 Taciang amate theampo nasiatak in kap uh a, Paul ngawngkoai in nam uh hi,   
\p
\v 38 Kuama in a maitang mu nawn ngawl tu, ci a kammal hang in khuangai tuansap uh hi. Taciang amate in tembaw kung dong tha uh hi.   
\c 21  
\s1 Miletas Pan Tyre  
\p
\v 1 Amate kung pan ka pai uh ciang in, tembaw taw a tangtan in ka pai uh a, Coos ka theng uh hi, a zingciang in Rhodes ka theng uh a, tua mun pan in Patara ka paisuak uh hi:   
\p
\v 2 Phoenicia pai tu tembaw ka mu uh a, a sung ka tum zawk uh ciang ka pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Cyprus ka mu uh ciang in veisang ka zuan uh a, Syria sangah ka pai uh hi, taciang Tyre ah ka tawlnga uh hi: banghangziam cile tua mun ah tembaw i puak van te khia uh hi.   
\s1 Tha Thiangtho in Paul Sia Jerusalem A Pai Tu Khak  
\p
\v 4 Taciang nungzui te taw ka kimu uh a, ni sali sung ka taam uh hi: amate in, Paul sia Jerusalem a pai tu hi ngawl hi, ci in Thaa tungtawn in son hi.   
\p
\v 5 Tua hun teng zawkciang in, ka pusuak kik uh a, ka paisuak uh hi; taciang amate a vekpi in a zite le a tate uh taw, khuapi puasang dong hong tha uh a: tuihui ah khupdin in thu ka ngen khawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 6 Taciang khat le khat ka kikhen zawk uh ciang, tembaw sung ka tum uh a, amate zong inn sangah cia uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Tyre pan in khualhaw ka man uh ciang in Ptolemais ka theng uh hi, taciang suapui te ka paupui uh a, amate taw ni khat sung ka om uh hi.   
\p
\v 8 A zingciang in koma Paul le a lawmte ka pai uh a, Caesarea ka theng uh hi: taciang thupha puak Philip innsung ah ka tum uh a, ka taam uh hi, Philip sia upa sali sung pan khat a hihi.   
\p
\v 9 Taciang Philip in tanu li nei hi, amate sia ngaknu thiangtho te hi a, mailam thu pualak uh hi.   
\s1 Kamsang Agabus  
\p
\v 10 Tua mun ah ni tampi sung ka taam uh hi, tua mun ah Judah ngam pan in Agabus a kici kamsang khat hong theng hi.   
\p
\v 11 Taciang ka kung uh ah hongpai ciang in, Paul i kawngkhau la a, ama khut le peang te hen hi, taciang, hi kawngkhau neipa sia Judah mite in Jerusalem ah hen tu a, Gentile mite khut sungah ap tu hi, ci in Tha Thiangtho in ci hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 12 Hi thu ka zak uh ciang in, koma le tua mun a omte in Paul sia Jerusalem pai ngawl tu in ka thum uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Tuazawkciang in Paul in, banghang in kap in ka thin hong nosak nu ziam? banghangziam cile ki hen tu bek hi ngawl, Jerusalem ah Topa Jesus min hang in thi tu zong ka ki nging khol zo hi, ci in zo hi.   
\s1 Paul Jerusalem Theng  
\p
\v 14 Taciang ka sonpui zawk ngawl uh ciang in, ka tawlnga uh a, Topa deina bang hi tahen, ka ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 15 Tua ni teng zawkciang in ka van te uh ka ki thoai uh a, Jerusalem ah ka pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 16 Caesarea a om nungzui pawlkhat te in zong hong zui uh a, ka ngia natu uh mun Syprus mi Mnason zong hong tonpui uh hi, Mnason sia a kipatcil pan kipan in nungzui khat a hihi.   
\p
\v 17 Jerusalem ka thet uh ciang in, suapui te in angtangtak in hong muak uh hi.   
\p
\v 18 A zingciang Paul taw James kungah ka tum uh a; upa te theampo zong om uh hi.   
\p
\v 19 Paul in amate nukset a, a tuan in Gentile te sung a nasep na tungtawn in Pathian i nasep nate pualak hi.   
\p
\v 20 Amate in tua thu a zak uh ciang in, Topa minthang pok uh a, thukham taw kisai a citak mama Judah mi tul tampi te in um uh hi; ci mu uh hi:   
\p
\v 21 Nangma in Moses thukham na nusia tu a, amate tate zong vunteap tan kul ngawl hi, taciang ngeina te zong a zui tu uh hi ngawl hi, ci in na hil hi, ci thu Gentile mite sungah a om Judah mite theampo tungah phawksak hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tua ahikom bang vawt tu khu ziam? mihonpi te hong ki kaikhop kul hamtang tu hi: banghangziam cile amate in nong thet hunlam he tu hi.   
\p
\v 23 Tua ahikom kong son uh bang in vawt in: amate tungah kiciamna a nei mi li ka nei uh hi;   
\p
\v 24 Amate taw pai tavun a, thiansuana vawt tavun, amate lu mettol hen a, a bo na dangka te zong piaksak in: taciang nangma taw kisai thu te sia bangma thupi ngawl hi; ahizong nangma vateak in thukham bang zui in nanungta hi, ci thu mi theampo in he tu hi.   
\p
\v 25 A um Gentile mite taw kisai in, tabang thu te bangma zui ngawl tu in, lai ka thak zo uh hi, ahihang milim te tung a kipia thisan, tawlsan in a ki ngo sa te le paktat nate pan in amate le amate kikeam tahen, ci hi.   
\p
\v 26 Tua ahikom Paul in a zingciang in mihing li te paipui a, amate taw thianthona vawt khawm uh hi, taciang biakinn sungah tum uh a, thianthona hun a bo tu ni le amate khatsim atu biakpiakna piak tu zong hil hi.   
\p
\v 27 Ni sali a bo ciang in, Asia ngam Judah mite biakinn sungah Paul a mu uh ciang in, mi theampo hanthawn uh a, Paul man uh hi,   
\p
\v 28 Israel mite awng, hong hu tavun: hisia pa in mun tatuam a om mi theampo, thukham le hi mun langpan in thuhil hi: tuabek domngawl in Greek mite zong biakinn sungah tumpui a, hi mun thiangtho ninsak hi, ci in au uh hi.   
\p
\v 29 Banghangziam cile amate in Ephesus khua mi Trophimus taw Jerusalem ah a mu ngei uh ahikom biakinn sungah tumpui hi, ci muangmaw uh hi.   
\p
\v 30 Taciang khuapi bup hong linglawng a, mipi te tai kheukho uh hi: taciang amate in Paul man uh a, biakinn sung pan in kaikeak uh hi: tasia pociang kongkha te khak siat hi.   
\p
\v 31 Amate in Paul that tu a paipui uh ciang in, tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa kungah, Jerusalem buppi buaina piang hi, ci thu theng hi.   
\p
\v 32 Ama in ngalkap te le zakhat uk ngalkapmang te sam pai a, mipi te sangah tai uh hi: taciang amate in tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa le ngalkap te a mu ciang in, Paul sia vel nawn ngawl in tawlnga hi.   
\p
\v 33 Tuazawkciang in tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa sia Paul kungah hongpai a, a mat zawkciang thikkol ni taw hen tu in thupia hi; taciang ama akua ziam, cile bangvawt ziam, ci dong hi.   
\p
\v 34 Taciang mihonpi sung pan in mi pawlkhat te in a tuam in au uh a, pawlkhat te in a tuam in au uh hi: tabang in ngalkap mangpa in buaina thu thiangtak in a tel thei ngawl hu in, Paul sia ngalkap inn huang sungah tumpui tu in thupia hi.   
\p
\v 35 Keallei tung a thet ciang in, ngalkap te in dom uh hi, banghangziam cile mipi te in nawm ngawp uh hi.   
\p
\v 36 Banghangziam cile mihonpi te in a nung pan zui uh a, hisia pa that vun, ci in au kawm uh hi.   
\s1 Paul Thusonna  
\p
\v 37 Paul sia ngalkap inn huang sungah a paipui tu uh ciang in, tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa kungah, kong paupui thei tu ziam? ci hi. Taciang ngalkap mangpa in Greek kam pau thei ni ziam?   
\p
\v 38 Nangma sia tu masia buaina vawt a, tualthat mi tul li duisung ah a paipui Egypt mi pa hi ngawl ni ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 39 Ahihang Paul in, keima sia Cilicia ngamsung ah khua thathong a hi ngawl, khuapi khat a hi Tarsus a om Judah mi ka hihi: taciang, hi mipi te tungah thuson hun nong piak natu kong thum hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 40 Ngalkap mangpa in thuson hun a piak ciang in, Paul sia keallei tungah ding a, mipi te a khut taw van hi. Taciang mipi te a thim khipkhep uh ciang in, amate tungah Hebrew kam taw thuson a,   
\c 22  
\p
\v 1 Suapui te le pa te awng, keima le keima ka ki hukna kammal te hong ngaisak tavun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 2 Amate in Hebrew kam taw a pau a zak uh ciang in, thim seseam uh a: taciang Paul in,   
\p
\v 3 Keima sia Judah mi tatak ka hihi, Silicia ngamsung ah khuapi khat ahi Tarsus ah ka suak hi, ahihang hi Jerusalem ah ka khang a, Gamaliel peang ah pu le pa te i ngeina a cing in hong hil hi, taciang tu ni in note bangma in Pathian sangah thalawptak in ka om ngei hi.   
\p
\v 4 Taciang Topa lampi\f + \fr 22:4 \fq Lampi \ft Thu umte a cinopna hi\f* a zui te vawtsia in, ka that hi, taciang numei le pasal ci ngawl in ka hen a, thong sungah ka ap hi.   
\p
\v 5 Thiampi sang le thudokpi te theampo in zong keima atu in tettipang hi: Damascus a omte hen tu le Jerusalem ah paipui in, danpiak natu lai te ka nga zawkciang in Damascus ah ka pai hi.   
\s1 Paul in A Kikhealna Thuson  
\r Hlh. 9:1-19; 26:12-18  
\p
\v 6 Taciang khual ka haw a, Damascus ka thet dektak sun hun pawl in, van pan in khuavak tang mama ka kimkot ah thakhathu in hong tang pimpem hi.   
\p
\v 7 Lei ah ka puk a, aw khat in, \wj Saul, Saul, banghang hong vawtsia ni ziam?\wj* hong ci ka za hi.   
\p
\v 8 Taciang keima in, Topa awng, nang akua ni ziam? ci in ka zo hi. Taciang Ama in keima tung ah, \wj Keima sia na vawtsiat Nazareth mi Jesus ka hihi, \wj* hong ci hi.   
\p
\v 9 Taciang ka kungah omte in khuavak sia mu takpi uh a, lau mama uh hi; ahihang keima hong paupui pa i aw a za bua uhhi.   
\p
\v 10 Taciang keima in, Topa awng, bang vawt tu khi ziam? ka ci hi. Topa in keima tung ah, \wj Tho in a, Damascus ah pai in; tua mun ah na vawt tu in kong sawl theampo te hong kison tu hi, \wj* hong ci hi.   
\p
\v 11 Tua a vanglian khuavak hang in khua ka mu thei bua hi, ka kung a omte in a khut uh taw hong kai uh a, Damascus ka theng hi.   
\p
\v 12 Tua mun ah Ananias a kici mi khat om hi, ama sia thukham bang in biakna sangah a kipumpiak hi a, tua mun ah a om Judah mite sungah a ki phatson pa khat a hihi,   
\p
\v 13 Tua Ananias sia ka kungah hongpai a, a din kawm in, suapui pa Sawl awng, khua mu kik in, hong ci hi. Tua hun lian in ama ka en hi.   
\p
\v 14 Taciang ama in ka kungah, i pu le pa te Pathian in Ama deina he tu le, mi thutang khat mu tu a, a kam pan a pusuak kammal ngai tu in hong teal zo hi.   
\p
\v 15 Banghangziam cile nangma sia na mu le na zak te ngual theampo tungah Ama tetti na hi tu hi.   
\p
\v 16 Taciang, tu in bang ngak ni ziam? tho in a, tui ki phum in, taciang na mawna te sil in a, Topa min sam in, hong ci hi.   
\s1 Gentile te Kung ah Thuhil Tu  
\p
\v 17 Tuazawkciang Jerusalem ka theng kik a, biakinn sungah thu ka nget laitak in, mang khat ka mu hi;   
\p
\v 18 Tua mun ah Topa in, \wj Manlang in, taciang Jerusalem pan manlangtak in pusuak in: banghangziam cile amate in keima taw kisai in na tettipanna hong sang ngawl tu uh hi, \wj* hong ci hi.   
\p
\v 19 Taciang keima in Topa awng, Nang hong umte synagogue sung theampo ah sat in thong ka taksak hi, ci amate in hong he hi:   
\p
\v 20 Taciang nangma ngalhang Stephen thisan a luan lai zong in, keima zong a hui ah ka ding a, a thina ah ka lungkim in a that te i puan te ka kepsak hi, ka ci hi.   
\p
\v 21 Taciang Topa in ka tung ah, \wj Pai in: banghangziam cile Gentile mite kung a khuala mama na ah kong paisak tu hi, \wj* hong ci hi.   
\s1 Paul Rome Mi  
\p
\v 22 Hi thu a son dong amate in ngai uh hi, tua zawkciang in a ngingtak in au uh a, hibang mihing that vun, leitung ah om heak tahen: banghangziam cile ama sia a nungta tu ki phu ngawl hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 23 Amate a au kawm in, a puan u te hawkkeak uh a, leivui van ah lawn ngawp uh hi.   
\p
\v 24 Tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa in Paul sia ngalkap inn huang sungah tumpui tu in thupia hi, taciang ama langpan in banghang mipi te au ziam? ci a heak natu in Paul sat a, thu dong tu in vaitha hi.   
\p
\v 25 Ahihang amate in savun khauhual taw a hen uh ciang in, Paul in zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa kungah, thu a kisit ngawl lai Rome ngam mi khat sat tu ngeina ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 26 Tua thu zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa in a zak ciang in, tul khat uk ngalkap mangpa tung ah, na nasep kidawm in: banghangziam cile hisia pa sia Rome mi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 27 Tuazawkciang in tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa hongpai a, nangma sia Rome mi na hi ziam? hong son tan, ci hi. Paul in, hi khi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 28 Taciang tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa in, Rome mi ka hina sia dangka tampi pia in ka nga hi, ci in zo hi. Taciang Paul in, ahihang kei ka sua pan in Rome mi ka hihi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 29 Tua zawk pociang in thudong tu te Paul kung pan paikhia uh hi: taciang tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa zong Paul sia Rome mi hi, ci a heak zawkciang in, patau mama hi, banghangziam cile ama in Paul man in a lehhen hang a hihi.   
\s1 Paul thudokpi te Mai ah  
\p
\v 30 A zingsang ciang in, Judah mite in Paul thusitna thu a tel thiang nop uh hu in, a hen nate sutsak uh a, thiampi lian te le, thudokpi\f + \fr 22:30 \fq thudokpi \ft Judah biakna makai te\f* te hongpai tu in thupia hi, taciang Paul paipui uh a, amate mai ah koi hi.   
\c 23  
\p
\v 1 Paul in thudokpi\f + \fr 23:1 \fq thudokpi \ft Judah biakna makai te\f* te tangtak in en a, u le nau te awng, tu ni dong Pathian mai ah sia le pha khentel theina thinsung pha taw ka nungta hi.   
\p
\v 2 Taciang thiampi sang Ananias sia Paul kungah ding a, Paul i muk pan sat tu in thupia hi.   
\p
\v 3 Tuazawkciang in Paul in, nang a ngo ki zut pangpi, Pathian in hong sat tu hi: banghangziam cile thukham bang in thukhen tu in to napi, banghang thukham taw ki lebul in keima sat tu in thu pia ni ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 4 Taciang Paul kungah a ding te in, Pathian i thiampi sang thusimngawl ni ziam? ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Tuasiaciang Paul in, suapui te awng, ama sia thiampi sang hi, ci ka he bua hi: banghangziam cile, na mihing lampui te phatngawlna kampau heak in, ci in ki atsa om hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 6 Ahihang Paul in pawlkhat te sia Saducee te hi a, a dang te sia Pharisee te hi, ci a heak ciang in, thudokpi te sungah, u le nau te awng, keima sia Pharisee ka hihi, Pharisee i tapa ka hihi: mithi te lametna le thawkikna thu dong tu in hongsam uh hi, ci au hi.   
\p
\v 7 Tabang in a son zawkciang in, Pharisee te le Saducee te ki laklaw ah ki thusik ngawl na hong om a: mihonpi kikhen siat hi.   
\p
\v 8 Banghangziam cile Saducee te in thawkikna, vantungmi le thaa om ngawl hi ci uh hi: ahihang Pharisee te in a vekpi in om hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 9 Nasiatak in au ngawp uh hi: taciang Pharisee te sung pan in thukhamhil te hong ding uh a, hisia pa a phatngawlna ka mu bua uh hi: ahihang thaa a hibale, vantungmi in paupui ahile, Pathian i do batu hi, ci in nasiatak in nial uh hi.   
\p
\v 10 A thu kisik ngawlna a nasiat seseam ciang in, tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa in, Paul sia amate in a laithap tu uh lau ahikom, ngalkap te tuaksuk in, amate sung pan lakeak tu le, ngalkap inn huang sungah paipui tu in thupia hi.   
\p
\v 11 Taciang a zingzan ciang in Topa sia paul kungah ding a, \wj Paul, hangsantak in om in: banghangziam cile Jerusalem ah keima thu tetti na pan bang in, Rome ah zong pang hamtang tu ni hi, \wj* ci hi.   
\s1 Paul That tu In Hanciam  
\p
\v 12 A zingsang ciang in, Judah mi pawlkhat te ki kaikhawm uh a, Paul a thalup mateng, an ne ngawl le tui dawn ngawl tu, ci in kiciamna vawt uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Hi kiciamna a vawt te sia mihing sawmli val pha uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Taciang amate thiampi lian te le ulian te kungah pai uh a, Paul ka thalup uh mateng bangma ne ngawl tu in kiciamna lianpi ka vawt zo uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 15 Tua ahikom tu in, noma le thudokpi te in tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa kungah, Paul thu a kicingzaw dong tu bang in na kungah a zingciang hong paipui tu in son vun: taciang kote in, a nai na pan, that tu in ka kinging khol tu uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 16 Taciang amate in tabang in suam tu a ngeal khop uh sia Paul i nau nu i tapa in a zak ciang in, ngalkap inn huang sungah tum a, Paul tungah son hi.   
\p
\v 17 Tuazawkciang in Paul in zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa te sung pan khat a kungah sam a, hi tangvalpa tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa kungah paipui tu in son hi: banghangziam cile ama in tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa tung sonnop nei hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 18 Tua ahikom tua ngalkap mangpa in tangvalpa sia tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa kungah paipui a, thongtak pa Paul in keima hong sam hi, taciang na kungah thuson tu a nei hi tangvalpa paipui tu in hong ngen hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 19 Tuazawkciang in tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa in tangvalpa a khut pan len a, a tuam in paipui hi, taciang bang hong son nuam ni ziam? ci in dong hi.   
\p
\v 20 Tangvalpa in, Judah mite in Paul thu a cingzaw dong tu bang in zingciang thudokpi te kungah paipui tu in hong ngen tu ci in, lungkim zo uh hi.   
\p
\v 21 Ahihang amate thu zui heak in: banghangziam cile mihing sawmli val in Paul suam nuam in pang uh hi, Paul a thalup uh mateng an ne ngawl le tui dawn ngawl tu in, kiciamna nei zo uh hi: taciang, amate sia nangma tung pan kamciam ngak in kinging khol in om uh hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tua ahikom tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa in tangval pa kungah, hi thu te nong son sia kuama tung son heak in, ci in vaitha a, ciasak hi.   
\s1 Paul Felix Kung ah Puak  
\p
\v 23 Taciang ama in zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa sam a, ngalkap za ni, siphu ngalkap sawm sali le teipi ngalkap za ni te tu zan nai kua in Caesarea pai tu in kinging khol vun;   
\p
\v 24 Paul i to tu nganhing te zong vaihawmsak vun a, taciang ngam uk Felix tungah bangma tat ngawl in puak vun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 25 Taciang hibang in laithak at hi:   
\p
\v 26 Claudius Lysias in a phabel ngam uk Felix tungah paupuina lai kong thak hi.   
\p
\v 27 Hisia pa sia Judah te in man uh a, a thalup tu uh hi napi: Rome mi hi, ci ka he a, ngalkap te taw pai in ka hun hi.   
\p
\v 28 Taciang amate i mawsiat na thu ka heak nop hu in thudokpi te kungah ka paipui hi:   
\p
\v 29 Ama a mawsiatna uh sia amate thukham thu ki dokna te hi, ci ka he hi, ahihang thina tak le thongtak khop tu mawna bangma nei ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 30 Taciang Judah mite in hisia pa suam sawm tawntung uh hi, ci thu hong ki son pociang in, na kungah hong puak khi hi, taciang a mawsiat te zong nangma mai ah son tu in thu ka pia hi, Na dam ta in, ci hi.   
\p
\v 31 Tuazawkciang in ngalkap te zong thupiakna bang in Paul la uh a, Antipatris ah zan ciang in paipui uh hi.   
\p
\v 32 A zingciang in siphu ngalkap te sia ama taw pai tu in nusia a, a dang te ngalkap huang sungah heakkik uh hi:   
\p
\v 33 Caesaria a thet uh ciang in, laithak sia ngam uk pa tungah ap uh a, Paul zong a mai ah ap uh hi.   
\p
\v 34 Ngam uk pa in laithak a sim zawkciang, koisung pan ziam, ci in dong hi, Taciang Caesaria pan hi, ci a heak ciang in;   
\p
\v 35 Nangma hong mawsiat te hong thet ciang in, na thu ka ngai kik tu hi, ci hi. Taciang Herod i thukhenna mun innpi sungah keam tu in thupia hi.   
\c 24  
\s1 Felix Mai ah Paul  
\p
\v 1 Ni nga zawkciang in thiampi sang Ananias sia ulian te le thusungpa Tertullus taw tuaksuk khawm uh a, Tertullus in paul thu sia ngam ukpa kungah son hi.   
\p
\v 2 Taciang Paul a sap uh ciang in Tertullus in mawsiat a, taciang Felix kungah, nangma hang in kilemna lianpi ka nei uh hi, na ukna tungtawn in hi mite tungah nong deisakna hang in phatna tampi nong vawtsak a,   
\p
\v 3 Tua thu te sia a tawntung in mun tatuam ah lungdamna taw in ka na sang uh hi, maw thinsung phabel Felix awng, ci hi.   
\p
\v 4 Ahitazong, hun saupi hong nawngkaisak ngawl in a tomno kong son tu thu thinsautak in nong ngaisak natu in kong thum hi.   
\p
\v 5 Banghangziam cile hisia pa sia ngual nawngkaisak, leitung theampo ah Judah mi theampo sungah ki nialna a piangsak le Nazaren pawl te makaipa ka mu zo uh hi:   
\p
\v 6 Ama sia biakinn ninsak tu in zong pai zo hi: ama ka man uh a, ka thukham uh bang in thu ka khen nuam uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Ahihang tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa Lysias hongpai a, ka khutsung uh pan in hong lakkeaksak hi,   
\p
\v 8 Ama a mawsiat te na kungah hongpai natu in thupia hi: nangma vateak in thu dong le te kote i mawsiatna hi thu te a vekpi in na he tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 9 Taciang Judah mite in zong hi thu te man hi, ci in thukim uh hi.   
\p
\v 10 Pual sia ngam uk pa in thuson tu in a khut taw a lak zawkciang in, nangma sia hi minam tungah kum tampi thukhenpa na hihi, ci ka heak ciang in lawptak in keima thu kong son tu hi:   
\p
\v 11 Jerusalem ah Pathian bia tu in ka pai zawk ni sawm le ni ni pha pheang hi, ci na he tu hi.   
\p
\v 12 Amate in biakinn sungah midang taw thu ka ki nial hong mu ngawl hi, taciang synagogue le khuapi sungah mipi te ka buaisak zong hong mu bua uh hi:   
\p
\v 13 Tu in hong mawsiatna thu te sia amate in tetti lak tu a he bua uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Ahihang hi thu sia na kungah kong pualak hi, ka pu le pa te Pathian ka bia a, thukham le kamsang te sungah a ki at theampo ka up hu in, amate in tua thu sia umkhial hi hong ci uh hi:   
\p
\v 15 Taciang mi thutang le thutang ngawl kibang tek in mithi te thawkikna om tu hi, ci amate in lametna a nei uh bangma in, keima zong Pathian tungah lametna ka nei hi.   
\p
\v 16 Taciang Pathian le mihing tungah khial tha ngawl in, sia le pha heak na thinsung thiangtho nei tu, ka hanciam theitawp in ka hanciam tawntung hi.   
\p
\v 17 Tu in kum tampi zawkciang ka mipui te kungah mizawng te huna le piakna te keng in ka pai hi.   
\p
\v 18 Biakinn sungah thianthona ka vawt zawkciang in, Asia ngam pan hongpai Judah mite in hong mu a, mihonpi le buaina om ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 19 Asia ngam pan hongpai Judah mite in keima mawsiatna tu nei ahile amate vateak na mai ah hongpai tu kilawm hi.   
\p
\v 20 Ahibale, hi mun a omte in, na phangawl ka vawt hong mu le, thudokpi te mai ah hong son tahen,   
\p
\v 21 Amate sungah ka din laitak in ka au na aw khat, mithi te thawkikna thu simngawl, tu in nangma in thu dong tu in nong sap natu thu dang om ngawl hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 22 Felix in hi thu te a zakciang in, tua lampi thu heakna a cingzaw in nei ahikom a ni khin a, tulkhat uk ngalkap mangpa Lysias hong thet ciang in, na thukhen kik tu khi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 23 Taciang zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa kungah, Paul keamcing tu le, a suaktatak in omsak natu ahizong, taciang ama khoi tu le a kung hongpai a lawm te kuama khak ngawl natu in thupia hi.   
\p
\v 24 Tua zawk a ngei ngawl in Felix a zi Drusilla taw hongpai hi, Drusilla sia Judah mi hi a, Paul sam in, Christ sungah a upna thu te ngai hi.   
\p
\v 25 Taciang Paul in thutang suana, kitekna le hong theng tu thukhenna thu te sonpui a, Felix sia lau in ling hi, taciang, tu in pai phot tan a, hun pha a om ciang in kong sam kik tu hi, ci in zo hi.   
\p
\v 26 Paul in a suatak thei natu in dangka hong pia tu hi, ci lamen ahikom Felix in Paul sia tu le tu in sam a, paupui tawntung hi.   
\p
\v 27 Ahihang kum ni zawkciang in Porcius Festas sia Felix inndoi sungah tum a: Judah mite lungkimsak tu dei ahikom, Felix in Paul sia pusua ngawl in thongsung ah nusia hi.   
\c 25  
\s1 Festus Mai ah Paul  
\p
\v 1 Festus sia tua ngamkhen sung a thet zawk ni thum ciang in, Caesarea pan Jerusalem ah paito hi.   
\p
\v 2 Tuazawkciang in thiampi sang le Judah mi makai te in Paul langpan na thu son in, thum uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Paul sia lamkal pan suam tu in pang uh a, a thalup nop uh hu in, Jerusalem ah puak tu in ngen uh hi.   
\p
\v 4 Ahihang Festus in, Paul sia Caesarea ah kepcing tu a hihi, ci in zo hi, taciang ama zong hai ngawl in Caesarea ah pai sawm hi.   
\p
\v 5 Tua ahikom note sung pan a pai thei tu te keima taw hongpai tavun a, Paul in phat ngawlna nei ahile mawsiat vun, ci hi.   
\p
\v 6 Festus sia amate sungah ni sawm val taam a, Caesarea pai hi; taciang a zingciang in thukhenna tokhum tungah to a, Paul paipui tu in thupia hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang Paul a thet ciang in, Jerusalem pan hongpai Judah mite a kimkot ah ding uh a, Paul tungah tetti a lak thei ngawl uh, thuak zawk a hi ngawl mawsiatna tampi suan uh hi.   
\p
\v 8 Paul in Judah mite thukham langpan in ahizong, biakinn langpan in ahizong, taciang Caesar langpan in ahizong, ka vawtkhial khat zong om ngawl hi, ci in zo hi.   
\p
\v 9 Ahihang Festus in Judah mite lungkimsak nuam ahikom, Paul kam zo kik a, Jerusalem ah pai in ka mai ah hi thu te taw kisai thukhen tu na uk ziam? ci hi.   
\p
\v 10 Tasia ciang Paul in, ka thu hong khensak tu a kilawm Caesar thukhenna tokhum ah ka ding hi: nangma in a thiangtak in na heaksa bangma in Judah mite tungah bangma a man ngawl vawt ngawl khi hi.   
\p
\v 11 Banghangziam cile keima sia thukham paltan, a hibale, thi tu kilawm mawna vawt ka hile, thi tu ka nial bua hi: ahihang hi mite i hong mawsiatna khat zong a man om ngawl ahile, kuama in amate tungah hong ap thei ngawl tu hi. Caesar tungah thusungkik\f + \fr 25:11 \fq thusungkik \ft a zuukhan\f* tu khi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 12 Festus in thudokpi te taw a kikup zawkciang in, Caesar kungah thusungkik tu ni ziam? Caesar kungah pai tu ni hi, ci in zo hi.   
\s1 Festas, Agrippa le Barnice Taw  
\p
\v 13 Ni pawlkhat sung a ngei zawkciang in kumpipa Agrippa le Bernice te Caesarea ah Festus nukset tu in hongpai uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Taciang amate Caesarea ah ni tampi a om zawk uh ciang in, Festus in kumpipa tung ah, Felix in thong a taksak khat om hi, ci in Paul thu pualak a:   
\p
\v 15 Jerusalem ah ka pai lai in, thiampi lian te le Judah mi ulian te in Paul i thu hong son uh a, ama thukhen tu in hong ngen uh hi.   
\p
\v 16 Amate kungah, mawsiatna a thuak pa sia a mawsiat te taw maitang kisi tu in, amate i mawsiatna thu taw kisai, ama atu thuson hun pia masa ngawl in, mi khatpo that tu in ap tu sia Rome mite i ngeina hi ngawl hi, ci in ka zo hi.   
\p
\v 17 Tua ahikom amate in hi mun ah hongpai uh ciang in, a zingciang khangkhan ngawl in thukhenna tokhum tungah ka to a, hisia pa hong paipui natu in thu ka pia hi.   
\p
\v 18 Ama a mawsiat te a din uh ciang in, ka ngaisut bang in mawsiatna bangma a son bua uh hi:   
\p
\v 19 Ahihang amate thuciin taw kisai in thudokna te, taciang Jesus a kici mi khat thi zo a, Paul in tua pa nungta hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 20 Taciang tabang thudokna te um ngawl ka hikom, hi thu te hang in thukhenna thuak tu in Jerusalem ah na pai tu ziam, ci ka dong hi.   
\p
\v 21 Ahihang Paul in Augustus mai ah thusung kik tu in hong ngen ahikom, Caesar kungah ka puak mateng keamcing tu in thu pia khi hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tasiaciang Agrippa in Festus tung ah, tua pa thu sia keima vateak zong in ka ngai tu hi, ci hi. Taciang Festus in zingciang in na ngai tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 23 A zingciang in, Agrippa le Bernice te sia thupitak in hongpai khawm uh hi, taciang tulkhat uk ngalkap mang te le khuapi sungah mi thupi te taw thu kikup ngai na mun inndoi sungah hong tum khawm uh a, Festus thupiakna bang in Paul paipui uh hi.   
\p
\v 24 Taciang Festus in, kumpipa Agrippa le hi mun ka kung a om mi theampo awng, hisia pa en vun, ama sia Jerusalem le hi mun ah om Judah mihonpi theampo in ka kungah a thu hong then uh a, ama sia a nungta tu kilawm ngawl hi, ci au uh hi.   
\p
\v 25 Ahihang ama in thi tu kilawm zadong a vawt bangma ka mu ngawl ciang in, ama in zong Augustus kungah thusungkik tu hong nget hu in, ama puak tu in thu ka khensat zo hi.   
\s1 Agrippa Mai ah Paul  
\p
\v 26 Ahihang ka topa kungah bangma at tu ka nei bua hi, Tua ahikom ama sia note i mai ah kong paipui hi, a tuan in kumpipa Agrippa awng, thu na dok zawkciang in, at tu nei thei tha tu khi hi.   
\p
\v 27 Banghangziam cile thongtak khat sia ama langpan in mawsiatna bangma kilang ngawlpi in puak tu phangawl tu in ka ngaisun hi, ci hi.   
\c 26  
\p
\v 1 Agrippa in Paul tung ah, nangma thu a son tu in hun kong pia hi, ci hi. Tuazawkciang in Paul in a khut phal in, ama thu hibang in son in zo hi:   
\p
\v 2 Kumpipa Agrippa awng, tu ni in Judah mite i hong mawsiatna hi thu te taw kisai in na mai ah keima vateak in hong zo tu ka hi man in, keima le keima hampha ka kisa hi:   
\p
\v 3 A tuan in nangma sia Judah mite ngeina te le thudokna theampo ah a telbel na hihi, ci ka he hi: tua ahikom thinsautak in nong ngaisak tu kong thum hi.   
\p
\v 4 Ka nolai pan kipan in ka nuntak zia sia, a masabel ka omna Jerusalem a om ka mipui Judah mite theampo in hong he hi;   
\p
\v 5 Amate in keima thu tettipang nuam uh hile, ka biakna uh i ngeina a khobel, Pharisee khat in ka nungta hi, ci sia a kipat pan ma in hong heak sa uh a hihi.   
\p
\v 6 Tu in Pathian in ka pu le pa te kungah a vawt kamciam i lametna hu in thukhenna thuak in ka ding hi:   
\p
\v 7 Tua hong thengpheang tu kamciam sungah lametna nei in ka mipui sawm le ni te in sun le zan tawlnga ngawl in, Pathian na ka seam uh hi. Tua lametna hang in, kumpi Agrippa awng, Judah mite in keima hong mawsak uh hi.   
\p
\v 8 Pathian in mithi te thosak kik tu hi, ci sia banghangin uptak ngawl thu in ngaisun nu ziam?   
\p
\v 9 Nazareth khua mi Jesus min langpan in na tampi vawt tu kilawm hi, ci in keima tatak in zong ngaisun takpi ngei khi hi.   
\p
\v 10 Tuathu sia keima in zong Jerusalem ah ka vawt ngei hi: thiampi lian te kung pan in sep thei na thu ka nga a, mithiangtho te thongsung ah ka khum hi; taciang amate thalup a thuak ciang zong, amate langpan in lungkimpui khi hi.   
\p
\v 11 Synagogue tatuam sungah zong ka vawtsia bul a, amate zawthawk vawt in Pathian min ka sonsiasak hi; taciang amate tungah ka thin-uk mama hu in, ngamdang khuapi ciangdong zong amate ka vawtsia ngei hi.   
\s1 Paul in A Kikhealna Thu Son  
\r Sawl 9:1-19; 22:6-16  
\p
\v 12 Tabang in thiampi lian te kung pan thuneina le thupiakna taw Damascus ka pai ciang in,   
\p
\v 13 Kumpipa awng, sun laitak in, lampi ah van pan in ni sang a tangzaw khuavak ka mu hi, tasia in keima le ka lawm te kimkot ah hong tang hi.   
\p
\v 14 Taciang ka vekpi in lei ah ka puk siat uh a, Hebrew kam taw, \wj Saul, Saul, banghang in hong vawtsia ni ziam? so zum khat sui ek tu sia nangma atu in haksak mama hi, \wj* ci aw khat in hong paupui ka za hi.   
\p
\v 15 Taciang keima in, akua ni ziam, Topa? ka ci hi. Taciang in, \wj Keima sia na vawtsiat Jesus ka hihi.\wj*   
\p
\v 16 \wj Ahihang tho in a, nangma peang tungah ding in: banghangziam cile hi ngealna atu in na kungah kong kilaak zo hi, na musa hi thu te le kong lak laitu thu te atu in naseam tu le tetti tu in kong vawt tu hi;\wj*   
\p
\v 17 \wj Nangma sia Judah mite le Gentile mite kung pan in kong suatak tu hi, \wj*   
\p
\v 18 \wj Amate i mit honsak tu ahizong, taciang khuamial pan in khuavak ah le Satan vangletna pan in Pathian kungah a heakkiksak tu, tabang in mawmaisak na nga tu le keima sungah upna tungtawn in a ki thiangthosak sa te sungah ngamhlua tu in, amate tungah tu in kong sawl hi, \wj* hong ci hi.   
\p
\v 19 Tua ahikom, maw kumpipa Agrippa awng, van pan in hongpai ka mangmuna thu ka nial bua hi.   
\p
\v 20 Amasabel in Damascus, taciang Jerusalem, taciang Judah ngamsung theampo le Gentile te kungah amate mawna ki sikkik a, Pathian kungah a heakkik thei natu le ki sikkik nataw a kiphu nasep te a sep natu in thu ka hil hi.   
\p
\v 21 Hi thu te hang in Judah mite in biakinn sungah hong man uh a, hong that nuam uh hi.   
\p
\v 22 Pathian panpuina ka nga hu in, tuni dong tatsat ngawl in a lian a no te tungah a kibang in tetti ka pang a, kamsang te le Moses in hong theng tu hi, ci a sonsa thu te simngawl a dang bangma ka son bua hi:   
\p
\v 23 Tua Christ sia thuak tu a, ama sia mithi te sung pan in a masabel thokik tu hi, taciang Judah mite le Gentile mite kungah khuavak thu tangsak tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 24 Taciang Paul in ama atu thu a son zawkciang in, Festus in aw ngingtak taw, Paul awng, na thin-am hi; a tamlei na sinna in na thin hong amsak hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 25 Ahihang Paul in, ka thin-am ngawl hi, a phabel Festus awng: ahihang thuman le ciimkam te ka pau hi.   
\p
\v 26 Banghangziam cile kumpipa in hi thu te he hi, a mai ah suaktatak in ka son hi: hi thu te theampo sia a kung pan in a ki phualseal khat zong om ngawl hi; banghangziam cile hi thu sia a kingsong mun ah a kivawt hi ngawl hi, ci sia keima in ka tel thiang hi.   
\p
\v 27 Kumpipa Agrippa awng, kamsang te na um ziam? Na um hi, ci ka he hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 28 Tasia ciang Agrippa in Paul kungah, Christian suak tu in hong kaizawn zo dektak ni hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 29 Taciang Paul in, nangma bek hi ngawl in, tu ni ka thusonna a za note theampo, dektak cibek hi ngawl in, thongtak thu simngawl keima bang tatak na hi thiangtho natu uh Pathian tungah ka thungetna a hihi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 30 Paul in thu a son zawkciang in, kumpipa, ngam uk Bernice te a topui te taw ding uh a:   
\p
\v 31 Amate a kingsong ah a pai zawk uh ciang in, hisia pa in thina tu kilawm le thongtak khop natu bangma vawt ngawl hi, ci amate sungah son tek uh hi.   
\p
\v 32 Tuazawkciang in Agrippa in Festus kungah, hisia pa in Caesar kungah thusungkik tu ngen hibale, suataksak tu hi napi, ci hi.   
\c 27  
\p
\v 1 Italy ah teambaw taw pai tu a ki khensat zawkciang in, amate in Paul le a dang thongtak te sia Augustus ngalkaphon sungah zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa Julius kungah ap uh hi.   
\p
\v 2 Taciang Adramyttium tembaw sungah ka tum uh a, Asia ngam tuipi dung zui in pai tu ka kipan uh hi; Macedonia ngam Thessalonica khua mi Aristarchus a kici khat zong kote taw hong ki thawl hi.   
\p
\v 3 A zingciang in Sidon ah ka tawlnga uh hi. Taciang Julius in Paul sia phat vawt a, a lawmte kungah pai in, ama le ama thathak la tu in suaktatak in ap hi.   
\p
\v 4 Tua mun pan in ka ki patkik uh ciang in, koma sangah hui hongpai ahikom Cyprus nuai pan in ka pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Cilicia le Pamphylia tuipi tungah ka pai zawk uh ciang, Lycia ngam khuapi Myra ka theng uh hi.   
\p
\v 6 Tua mun ah zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa in Italy a pai tu Alexandria tembaw mu a; tua tembaw sungah hong tumsak hi.   
\p
\v 7 Taciang dadam in ni tampi sung ka pai zawk uh ciang in, Cnidus tangtan haksatak in ka theng uh hi, hui in hong khak ahikom in, Crete tuikul nuai pan Salmone ah a tangtan in ka pai uh hi;   
\p
\v 8 Taciang haksatak in ka kantan uh a, A Pha Tembaw Tawlngakna Mun, a kici na mun ka theng uh hi; tua mun sia Lasea khuapi taw ki nai hi.   
\p
\v 9 Tu in hun tampi ka zak zawk uh ciang in, antan hun zong bo zo a, tembaw taw khualhaw tu sia lauhuai hi, ci in Paul in kidopna tu son hi,   
\p
\v 10 Taciang amate tung ah, hi tembaw taw khualhaw tu sia vanpuak te le tembaw atu bek hi ngawl in, eite nuntakna dong in haksatna le siatsuana tampi om tu hi, ci i he hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 11 Ahihang zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa in Paul i thuson te sang in, tembaw hawlpa le a neipa thu um zaw hi.   
\p
\v 12 Tua tembaw tawlngakna mun sia phalbi hun sung om natu phangawl ahikom, ahi thei le Phenice thet dong paisuak tu a, tua mun ah phalbi sung theampo om tu a tamzaw in ngaisutna pia uh hi; tasia sia Crete tembaw tawlngakna mun hi a, nitum na thangsang le nitumna saksang maingat in om hi.   
\p
\v 13 Taciang thangsang pan hui in hongseam va hiau a, amate in a ngealna theng zo hi, ci ngaisun uh a, Crete nai na pan in pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 14 Ahihang a hai ngawl in, Euroclydon a kici sumpei bang in huipi hong ki nuai ngawp hi.   
\p
\v 15 Ka tembaw uh sia hui in nuaicip a, tua hui nawk zo ngawl ahikom in, hui in a ukna mun theampo ah hong paipui hi.   
\p
\v 16 Clauda a kici tuikul nuai pan in ka pai uh laitak in, haksatak in ngunkuang ka dom uh a;   
\p
\v 17 Tembaw tungah ka domto zawk uh ciang in, tembaw a kho natu in ngunkuang sia khau taw hen hi; taciang senneal tam na mun ah tembaw awk tu lau uh ahikom tembaw puankhak te khiasuk uh a, hui in a uk na munpo ah hong paipui hi.   
\p
\v 18 Huipi in nasiatak in hong nuaicip veve ahikom in, a zingciang in tembaw zaangsak uh hi;   
\p
\v 19 Taciang ni thum na ciang in kote i khut vateak taw in tembaw vanpuak te ka vawk uh hi.   
\p
\v 20 Taciang ni tampi sung ni le aksi te ki mu nawn ngawl a, huipi nasiatak in hong vak lai ciang in, ka suatak natu uh lametna theampo bosiat zo hi.   
\p
\v 21 Ahihang ngei mama an a ki ngawl zawkciang, Paul sia amate laizang ah ding a, ka thu nong man tu uh hi napi, Crete pan in pai ngawl hileang, hi haksatna le supna te i thuak batu hi.   
\p
\v 22 Tuin thinnuamtak in om tu in kong hanthawn hi: banghangziam cile tembaw simngawl, note sungah mihing nuntakna khat zong bo ngawl tu hi.   
\p
\v 23 Banghangziam cile tuzan in keima hong nei le a na ka sepsak Pathian vantungmi ka kungah hong ding a,   
\p
\v 24 Paul awng, lau heak in; nangma sia Caesar mai ah hong paipui hamtang tu khi hi: taciang, en in, nangma taw tembaw tung khualhaw te theampo Pathian in hong pia zo hi, hong ci hi.   
\p
\v 25 Tua ahikom, thinnuam in om vun: banghangziam cile Pathian in keima hong sonsa bang in tangtung tu hi, ci ka um hi.   
\p
\v 26 Ahihang tuikul khatpo ah hui in hong vawk hamtang tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 27 Ahihang zan sawm le zan ni na ciang in, Adria tuipi sungah loksuk lokto in hong paipui a, zankim laitak pawl in tembaw naseam te in tuihui lei ki nai zo hi, ci muangmaw uh hi;   
\p
\v 28 Taciang tui a te uh ciang in pi za le kul thuk hi, ci he uh hi: taciang tawm a khuala zawhiat a pai zawkciang in te kik a, pi sawmkua thuk hi, ci he uh hi.   
\p
\v 29 Tuazawkciang in tembaw in suangpi a taithak tu a lau uh hu in, tembaw nungsang pan thikkapui li khia uh a, khuavak natu in thu ka ngen khawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 30 Taciang tembaw naseam te tembaw sung pan in a puasang ah tai sawm uh a, ngunkuang tuipi sungah a khiak uh ciang in, tembaw lusang pan in thikkapui te khia tu bang in ki omsak uh hi,   
\p
\v 31 Paul in zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa le ngalkap te kungah, hi mite tembaw sung a om nginge bua ahile, kuama suakta thei ngawl tu nu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 32 Tuazawkciang in ngalkap te in ngunkuang khii na khau te sattan a, ngunkuang khia uh hi.   
\p
\v 33 Khuavak dektak ciang in, Paul in amate theampo an ne tu in thum a, tuni sia a kizom in antang in, bangma ne ngawl in na om uh ni sawm le ni li na hi zo hi.   
\p
\v 34 Tua ahikom an tawmtek ne tu in kong thum hi: banghangziam cile hisia sia na dam natu uh a hihi: banghangziam cile na lu tung uh pan in samzam khat zong tong ngawl tu hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 35 Tabang a ci zawkciang in, anluum la a, amate theampo i mai ah Pathian tung lungdam a ko zawkciang in: balnen in ne hi.   
\p
\v 36 Tuazawkciang in amate theampo thinnuam tek uh a, an tawmtek ne uh hi.   
\p
\v 37 Tembaw sungah ka vekpi uh in mihing zani le sawm sali le luk ka pha uh hi.   
\p
\v 38 Amate an a kham in a neak tek zawk uh ciang in, zungtang te tuipi sungah khuasuk uh a, tembaw vanzaangsak hi.   
\s1 Tembaw Lal  
\p
\v 39 Khua hong vak ciang in, koisung ngam ci a he bua uh hi: ahihang amate in kingkoai khat sia valbo taw ki thua mu uh a, a suakthei le tua sungah tembaw tumpui sawm uh hi.   
\p
\v 40 Taciang thikkapui te sattan in tuipi sungah nusia hi, taciang tembaw khiina khau te sut uh a, tembaw maisang puankhak sia hui i mut tu in khak uh hi, taciang tembaw sia tuihui sangah paisak hi.   
\p
\v 41 Tembaw sia tuipi ni ki siktua na mun ah theng a, senneal tungah awksak uh hi; taciang a maisang sia senneal sungah tumsak uh a, tung thei ngawl in awk hi, ahihang a nungsang sia tuihual hat mama in tamthamsak hi.   
\p
\v 42 Ngalkap te, thongtak te that siat tu in kikum uh hi, tabang hibale thongtak te tui op tu a, tai siat tu hi.   
\p
\v 43 Ahihang zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa in, Paul a ngup nop hu in, amate i ngealna khak a; tui op thiam peuma amasabel in tuisung ah leangsuk tu le tuihui dong op tu in thupia hi:   
\p
\v 44 A tanglai pawlkhat te sia thingpheak tung le pawlkhat te tembaw bek thingpheak te tung pan in tuihui ah bangma tat ngawl in theng siat uh hi.   
\c 28  
\s1 Melita Tuikul Theng  
\p
\v 1 Amate a suatak zawk uh ciang in, tua tuikul sia Melita kici hi, ci he uh hi.   
\p
\v 2 Ngua hong zu a, khuasik mama ahikom in mimawl\f + \fr 28:2 \fq Mimawl \ft Luzai te, barbarian\f* te in mei hong tawsak uh a, ka vekpi in hong sang in, kote hong phatvawt mama uh hi.   
\p
\v 3 Taciang Paul in thing lomkhat hong toai in, meisung ah a bumsuk ciang, sa ahikom in ngul khat hong pusuak a, Paul i khut tungah hong ki vial hi.   
\p
\v 4 Taciang mimawl te in Paul i khut ah a ngu hang mama ngulpui in pom ci a mu uh ciang in, hisia pa sia tualthat hi nanak tu hi, tuipi sung pan suakta napi, phulakna in nungtasak tuan ngawl hi, ci in amate kikum uh hi.   
\p
\v 5 Taciang Paul in tua nganhing sia meisung ah thing a, bangma tat ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 6 Ahihang amate in banghun ciang hong tumkeak tam maw, a hibale, banghun ciang upmawk ngawlpi, puk in a thi tam maw, ci in encik uh hi: ahihang hun saupi sung a etcik zawk uh ciang in, bangma a phatmawk ngawl ciang, amate in a ngaisutna uh khealkik a, hisia pa sia pathian hi, ci uh hi.   
\p
\v 7 Tua mun ah tuikul ukpa in lo ngam nei a, tua pa min sia Publius kici hi; ama in phatak in hong sang a, ni thum sung hong taamsak hi.   
\p
\v 8 Taciang in, Publius i pa sia cisa natna le ngilsan vei in lum hi: Paul a kungah pai a, thungen in a tungah khut nga a, damsak hi.   
\p
\v 9 Tua ahikom hibang a vawt zawkciang in, tuikul sung a natna nei theampo zong hongpai uh a, dam uh hi:   
\p
\v 10 Amate in letsong tam mama hongpia uh a, ka din uh ciang in ka kisap uh na tampi tembaw tungah hong koisak uh hi.   
\s1 Rome Khua Ah Paul Theng  
\p
\v 11 Tha thum zawkciang phalbi sung theampo tuikul ah ka om uh a, Castor le Pollux ci khiakna nei Alexandria tembaw taw ka pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 12 Syracuse ah ka tawlnga uh a, tua mun ah ni thum sung ka om uh hi.   
\p
\v 13 Tua mun pan pusuak in ka kiimveal uh a, Rhegium ka theng uh hi: ni khat zawkciang in, thangsang pan hui hong va ahikom, a zingciang in Puteoli ka theng uh hi:   
\p
\v 14 Tua mun ah suapui te ka mu uh a, amate in ni sali om tu in hong ngen uh hi: tabang in Rome sangah ka pai uh hi.   
\p
\v 15 Rome a om suapui te in ka thu a zak uh ciang in, koma muak tu in Appii vanzuak na le zintun inn thum kici na pan in hongpai uh hi: taciang Paul in amate a mu ciang in, Pathian pok a, thinnuam in om uh hi.   
\p
\v 16 Rome ka thet uh ciang in, zakhat uk ngalkap mangpa in thongtak te thonginn cing topa kungah ap hi: ahihang Paul sia ama nguak in a cingtu ngalkap khat taw omsak hi.   
\s1 Rome Khua ah Paul i Nasep  
\p
\v 17 Ni thum zawkciang in, Paul in Judah makai te munkhat ah kaikhawm a: hongpai uh ciang in, amate tung ah, u le nau te awng, mite le ka pu le pa te ngeina langpan in ka vawt na bangma om ngawl hi napi, Jerusalem pan in thongtak tu in Rome mite khut sungah hong ap uh hi.   
\p
\v 18 Thu hong dong uh a, thina tak mawna bangma vawt ngawl ci mu a hi uh man in, Rome mite in hong suatak nuam uh hi.   
\p
\v 19 Ahihang Judah mite in a nial uh ciang in, ka mipui te ka mawsak tu hi ngawl napi, Caesar kungah thusungkik ngawl in suak thei nawn ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 20 Tua ahikom, hi thu hang in noma taw kimu tu le paupui tu in hong sam ka hihi: Israel te lametna atu in thikkol thak ka thuak hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 21 Taciang amate in Paul tung ah, nangma taw kisai in Judah ngam pan laithak nga ngawl khu hi, taciang suapui te sung pan in hongpai uh a na phatngawlna thu a son khat zong om ngawl hi.   
\p
\v 22 Ahihang na ngaisutna ka za nuam uh hi: banghangziam cile hite pawl te thu taw kisai in, mun tatuam ah midangte langpan in kampau hi, ci ka he uh hi, ci uh hi.   
\s1 Paul in Rome Ah Thuhil  
\p
\v 23 Taciang amate in Pual sia nikhat a ciangtansak zawk uh ciang in, a tunna ah mi tampi hongpai uh a; tuate tungah Pathian kumpingam thu tettipang in hilcian hi, Moses thukham le kamsang laibu te sung pan in Jesus thu taw kisai in zingpan kipan nitak sang dong hanthotna nei hi.   
\p
\v 24 Taciang a son thu te sia mi pawlkhat te in um uh a, pawlkhat te in a um bua uh hi.   
\p
\v 25 Ama te sungah a thu uh a kisik ngawl uh ciang in, pai uh a, tua zawkciang in Paul in thu khat son hi, Tha Thiangtho in kamsang Isaiah tungtawn in i pu le pa te tung ah,   
\p
\v 26 Hi mite tungah pai tan a, son in, a zak in za napi, na tel bua uh hi; a mu in mu napi, na tel thei tuan bua uh hi:   
\p
\v 27 Banghangziam cile, hi minam te sia a mit uh te khua mu ngawl, a bil uh te khua za ngawl, a thinsung in bangma tel thiam ngawl in a nuntak dan te zong ki kheal ngawl uh ahikom in, a natna uh te zong ka damsak ngawl dong in amate sia a thin uh pui lei a, a bil uh te in khua za hak bek domngawl a mit uh te zong thi siat hi, ci in a mantak in son hi.   
\p
\v 28 Tua ahikom Pathian i ngupna sia Gentile mite tungah ki puak zo a, amate in tua thu ngai tu uh hi, ci in kong phawksak hi, ci hi.   
\p
\v 29 Paul in hi thu te a son zawkciang in, Judah mite pai uh a, amate sungah nasiatak in thu kikum uh hi.   
\p
\v 30 Paul sia a sap tawm inn ah kum ni sung om hi, taciang a kungah hongpai theampo sang a,   
\p
\v 31 Pathian kumpingam thupha hil le Topa Jesus Christ taw kisai thu te hangsantak in hil a, kuama in khaktan ngawl hi.   